{"data":[{"date":"15:33 18/07","title":"World Cup 2018 qua nh\u1eefng con s\u1ed1 ti\u00eau bi\u1ec3u","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/18/wc.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea ti\u00eau bi\u1ec3u World Cup 2018, gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1eeba kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec1 \u0110T Ph\u00e1p.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<h2><strong><br>\r\nWorld Cup 2018 qua nh\u1eefng con s\u1ed1<br>\r\n</strong></h2>\r\n<strong><br>\r\n519</strong> &ndash; 3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t World Cup 2018 ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 chi\u1ec1u cao t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 519cm (Modric &ndash; 172cm, Hazard 173cm, Griezmann 174cm), l\u00e0 b\u1ed9 ba l\u00f9n nh\u1ea5t l\u1ecbch s\u1eed; ch\u1ec9 h\u01a1n k\u1ef3 World Cup 1990 v\u1edbi Toto Schillaci, Lothar Matthaus v\u00e0 Diego Maradona (cao 512cm).<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea ti\u00eau bi\u1ec3u World Cup 2018 \u1ea3nh 1\" title=\"Modric \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00ecnh ch\u1ecdn l\u00e0 C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t World Cup 2018\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/16/Rakitic-noi-ve-Modric-tri-an-sau-ky-World-Cup-2018-dang-tu-hao-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Modric \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00ecnh ch\u1ecdn l\u00e0 C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t World Cup 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div><br>\r\n<strong>135 &ndash;</strong> Ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, 2 HLV Oscar Tabarez c\u1ee7a Uruguay v\u00e0 Fernando Santos c\u1ee7a B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 &ldquo;c\u1ef1u chi\u1ebfn binh&rdquo;, v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9 tu\u1ed5i t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 135 tu\u1ed5i. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y khi\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa h\u1ecd tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u00e0 nh\u1ea5t tr\u00ean c\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ecb thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>72,5 &ndash; </strong>T\u1ed5ng qu\u00e3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng di chuy\u1ec3n c\u1ee7a Ivan Perisic t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0o. Gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u0103m 2014, ng\u01b0\u1eddi di chuy\u1ec3n nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 Thomas Muller (84km), c\u00f2n con s\u1ed1 n\u00e0y \u1edf n\u0103m 2010 l\u00e0 Xavi (80km).<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>48 &ndash; </strong>\u0110\u00e3 48 n\u0103m tr\u00f4i qua, World Cup m\u1edbi ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn m\u1ed9t m\u00e0n l\u1ed9i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng trong t\u00ecnh th\u1ebf b\u1ecb d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc 2 b\u00e0n, khi B\u1ec9 h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 3-2.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>40 &ndash;</strong> \u0110\u00e3 40 n\u0103m tr\u00f4i qua, tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft World Cup lu\u00f4n c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Inter Milan ho\u1eb7c Bayern Munich. \u1ede gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u0103m nay, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a c\u1ea3 2 CLB n\u00e0y (Perisic, Brozovic &ndash; Inter v\u00e0 Tolisso &ndash; Bayern).</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/khong-phai-nhan-to-m-day-moi-la-2-clb-thong-tri-lich-su-world-cup-421-191023.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/12/ivan.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/khong-phai-nhan-to-m-day-moi-la-2-clb-thong-tri-lich-su-world-cup-421-191023.html\">Kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i &ldquo;nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 M&rdquo;, \u0111\u00e2y m\u1edbi l\u00e0 2 CLB th\u1ed1ng tr\u1ecb l\u1ecbch s\u1eed World Cup</span><br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00f2ng b\u00e1n k\u1ebft, Man United, Chelsea v\u00e0 Man City c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ebfn 7 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f2n s\u00f3t l\u1ea1i, trong khi Tottenham nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t v\u1edbi 8 ng\u01b0\u1eddi. Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u0111\u00e2y m\u1edbi l\u00e0 2 CLB c\u00f3...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<strong>21h10&rsquo; &ndash;</strong> T\u1ed5ng th\u1eddi gian Cris Ronaldo (8 tr\u1eadn) v\u00e0 Leo Messi (6 tr\u1eadn) thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp World Cup, kh\u00f4ng ghi n\u1ed5i b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng n\u00e0o.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>18 &ndash;</strong> Sau 18 tr\u1eadn ch\u00e2u \u00c1 to\u00e0n thua Nam M\u1ef9, r\u1ed1t cu\u1ed9c Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n c\u0169ng ch\u1ea5m d\u1ee9t con s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00e1ng bu\u1ed3n n\u00e0y, khi Nh\u1eadt h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c Colombia 2-1.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>14,3 &ndash;</strong> \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 c\u1ee7a David De Gea, th\u1ea5p h\u01a1n b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n n\u00e0o, khi anh ch\u1ec9 c\u1ee9u thua \u0111\u00fang 1 l\u1ea7n, th\u1ee7ng 6 b\u00e0n sau 4 tr\u1eadn. \u0110\u1ec3 so s\u00e1nh, con s\u1ed1 n\u00e0y c\u1ee7a Kasper Schmeichel l\u00e0 91,3%, c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng 21/23 c\u00fa s\u00fat.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea ti\u00eau bi\u1ec3u World Cup 2018 \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"De Gea vs Nga\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/2/Tay-Ban-Nha-bi-loai-La-Roja-be-tac-va-noi-that-vong-De-Gea-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Nh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea ti\u00eau bi\u1ec3u World Cup 2018: Th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng De Gea</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong><br>\r\n12 &ndash;</strong> S\u1ed1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng pha ph\u1ea3n l\u01b0\u1edbi \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, nhi\u1ec1u g\u1ea5p \u0111\u00f4i n\u0103m 2014 (6 l\u1ea7n).<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>11 &ndash;</strong> Harry Maguire c\u00f3 t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 11 pha d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n h\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t ng\u00f4i sao tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng nh\u01b0 Jesus (10), Modric (10), Sterling (10), Lewandowski (9), Mbappe (8),&hellip; C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 Neymar v\u1edbi 27 l\u1ea7n.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>10 &ndash;</strong> B\u1ec9 s\u1edf h\u1eefu 10 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 kh\u00e1c nhau l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng, nhi\u1ec1u ngang Ph\u00e1p 1982 v\u00e0 Italia 2006.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>7 &ndash;</strong> Mexico g\u1ee5c ng\u00e3 \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8 trong 7 l\u1ea7n tham d\u1ef1 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp.<br>\r\n&nbsp;<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/ngap-tran-anh-che-ve-man-an-mung-an-tuong-cua-tong-thong-phap-421-191507.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/18/ngap-tran-anh-che-ve-man-an-mung-an-tuong-cua-tong-thong-phap.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/ngap-tran-anh-che-ve-man-an-mung-an-tuong-cua-tong-thong-phap-421-191507.html\">Ng\u1eadp tr\u00e0n \u1ea3nh ch\u1ebf v\u1ec1 m\u00e0n \u0103n m\u1eebng \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a T\u1ed5ng th\u1ed1ng Ph\u00e1p</span><br>\r\nD\u00f9 tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 \u0111\u00e3 k\u1ebft th\u00fac \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u00e0i ng\u00e0y, nh\u01b0ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh T\u1ed5ng th\u1ed1ng Ph\u00e1p Macron \u0103n m\u1eebng v\u1eabn khi\u1ebfn nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u00edch th\u00fa.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/world-cup-2018-nhung-tran-cau-va-khoanh-khac-dang-nho-nhat-421-191457.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/17/world-cup-2018-nhung-tran-cau-va-khoanh-khac-dang-nho-nhat.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/world-cup-2018-nhung-tran-cau-va-khoanh-khac-dang-nho-nhat-421-191457.html\">World Cup 2018: Nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u v\u00e0 kho\u1ea3nh kh\u1eafc \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1edb nh\u1ea5t</span><br>\r\nK\u1ef3 \u0111\u1ea1i h\u1ed9i tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i, v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c t\u00ecm ra nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng l\u00e0 th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Didier Deschamps, d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng kho\u1ea3nh kh\u1eafc World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1388","checkdouble":"191516"},{"date":"15:13 18/07","title":"Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn kh\u00f3 c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1edbi \u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/5/tien-dung-thua-nhan-kho-canh-tranh-voi-van-lam-tai-asiad-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chia s\u1ebb v\u1edbi gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng, B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn '\u0111\u00e0n anh' \u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e1ng g\u1eddm nh\u01b0ng anh s\u1ebd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh su\u1ea5t b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh t\u1ea1i \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam.</h2><h2>Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao \u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m</h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Trong l\u00e0ng b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam, B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng\u00a0v\u00e0 \u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m \u0111ang l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao nh\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n nay. V\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn c\u1ea3 hai c\u00f3 t\u00ean trong danh s\u00e1ch s\u01a1 b\u1ed9 \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho ASIAD 2018.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p>V\u0103n L\u00e2m kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 h\u01a1n Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng \u1edf th\u1ec3 h\u00ecnh, kinh nghi\u1ec7m m\u00e0 anh c\u0169ng \u0111ang thi \u0111\u1ea5u r\u1ea5t \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o CLB H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng, trong khi \u0111\u00f3 t\u1ea1i FLC Thanh H\u00f3a, B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb v\u00e0 m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV \u0110\u1ee9c Th\u1eafng tr\u1ecdng d\u1ee5ng tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i trong nh\u1eefng v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn kh\u00f3 c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1edbi V\u0103n L\u00e2m h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn kh\u00f3 c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1edbi V\u0103n L\u00e2m h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/5/tien-dung-thua-nhan-kho-canh-tranh-voi-van-lam-tai-asiad-2018.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>\u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m v\u00e0 B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng s\u1ebd c\u1ea1nh tranh kh\u1ed1c li\u1ec7t cho su\u1ea5t b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>V\u00ec th\u1ebf, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb \u1edf ASIAD 2018 l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn. Tuy nhi\u00ean th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh sinh n\u0103m 1997 c\u0169ng th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m \u2018\u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i\u2019 V\u0103n L\u00e2m trong cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua gi\u00e0nh su\u1ea5t b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p>Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng chia s\u1ebb \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y v\u1edbi gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng: \u201cKhi nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u1ea5y b\u00e1o c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n, t\u00f4i r\u1ea5t vui v\u00e0 c\u0169ng r\u1ea5t \u00e1p l\u1ef1c v\u00ec th\u1ea5y b\u1ea3o l\u00e0 l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y g\u1ecdi kh\u00e1 l\u00e0 \u0111\u00f4ng nh\u01b0ng l\u1ea1i l\u1ea5y r\u1ea5t \u00edt \u0111\u1ec3 sang Indonesia. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p>V\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi t\u1ed1t v\u00e0 t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i ph\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ea5u r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u. Anh L\u00e2m hi\u1ec7n \u0111ang l\u00e0 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n s\u1ed1 1 c\u1ee7a Vi\u1ec7t Nam. V\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea5y l\u00e0 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed m\u00e0 n\u1ebfu t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u01a1i ch\u00ednh th\u00ec t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i anh \u1ea5y, nh\u01b0ng s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n \u0111\u1ea5y!\u201d.<o:p></o:p><br>\r\n<br>\r\nS\u1ef1 c\u1ea1nh tranh c\u1ee7a V\u0103n L\u00e2m v\u00e0 Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng n\u1ebfu nh\u00ecn v\u1ec1 h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u00edch c\u1ef1c, s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t c\u00f3 l\u1ee3i cho U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam b\u1edfi \u0111\u00f3 s\u1ebd gi\u00fap HLV Park Hang Seo l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u01b0\u1eddi t\u00e0i nh\u1ea5t cho \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p><br>\r\nNhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ea3 Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng, V\u0103n L\u00e2m v\u00e0 th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh th\u1ee9 3 Nguy\u1ec5n V\u0103n Ho\u00e0ng (S\u00e0i G\u00f2n) s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1eed s\u1ee9c t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng di\u1ec5n ra t\u1eeb 3-7/8 t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n v\u1eadn \u0111\u1ed9ng M\u1ef9 \u0110\u00ecnh. \u0110\u00e2y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 b\u00e0i ki\u1ec3m tra \u0111\u1ec3 xem ai s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ee7 b\u1ea3n l\u0129nh nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc khung g\u1ed7.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/goc-nhin-thay-park-se-cham-van-lam-hay-bui-tien-dung-cho-asiad-2018-168-187794.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/5/goc-nhin-thay-park-se-cham-van-lam-hay-bui-tien-dung-cho-asiad-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/goc-nhin-thay-park-se-cham-van-lam-hay-bui-tien-dung-cho-asiad-2018-168-187794.html\">G\u00f3c nh\u00ecn: Th\u1ea7y Park s\u1ebd ch\u1ea5m V\u0103n L\u00e2m hay B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng cho ASIAD 2018?</span><br>\r\n\u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m v\u00e0 B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng \u0111ang l\u00e0 hai th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n thi \u0111\u1ea5u n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam. Nh\u01b0ng li\u1ec7u HLV Park Hang Seo s\u1ebd ch\u1ecdn ai b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh cho \u0110T Olympic...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/bi-cam-quan-hlv-quang-nam-het-loi-khen-ngoi-tai-nang-cua-dang-van-lam-168-189294.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/4/bi-cam-quan-hlv-quang-nam-het-loi-khen-ngoi-tai-nang-cua-dang-van-lam.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/bi-cam-quan-hlv-quang-nam-het-loi-khen-ngoi-tai-nang-cua-dang-van-lam-168-189294.html\">B\u1ecb c\u1ea7m ch\u00e2n, HLV Qu\u1ea3ng Nam h\u1ebft l\u1eddi khen ng\u1ee3i t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a \u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m</span><br>\r\nTrong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u di\u1ec5n ra t\u1ea1i Tam K\u1ef3 chi\u1ec1u 22/6, CLB Qu\u1ea3ng Nam \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i \u2018c\u01b0a \u0111i\u1ec3m\u2019 tr\u01b0\u1edbc H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng FC c\u1ee7a \u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m. V\u00e0 ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn, HLV Ho\u00e0ng V\u0103n Ph\u00fac...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/thu-mon-dang-van-lam-nhan-mua-loi-khen-sau-tran-gap-sai-gon-fc-168-187731.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/4/thu-mon-dang-van-lam-nhan-mua-loi-khen-sau-tran-gap-sai-gon-fc.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/thu-mon-dang-van-lam-nhan-mua-loi-khen-sau-tran-gap-sai-gon-fc-168-187731.html\">Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m nh\u1eadn m\u01b0a l\u1eddi khen sau tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC</span><br>\r\nSau m\u00e0n thi \u0111\u1ea5u nh\u01b0 l\u00ean \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m tr\u01b0\u1edbc khung g\u1ed7 H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Vi\u1ec7t ki\u1ec1u n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi khen c\u00f3 c\u00e1nh t\u1eeb gi\u1edbi chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>Minh Long (TTVN)</p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1387","checkdouble":"191517"},{"date":"15:48 18/07","title":"S\u1ed1ng c\u00f9ng World Cup 2018 s\u1ed1 33: Kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i Messi, \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 2 nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 M10 hay nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/2/song-cung-world-cup-2018-so-33-khong-phai-messi-day-la-2-nhan-to-m10-hay-nhat-the-gioi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>World Cup 2018 ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn s\u1ef1 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng c\u1ee7a hai ng\u00f4i sao \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1ecdi l\u00e0 M10 nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i Messi nh\u01b0 nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi ngh\u0129. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ai? H\u00e3y c\u00f9ng theo d\u00f5i S\u1ed1ng c\u00f9ng World Cup 2018 s\u1ed1 33 \u0111\u1ec3 bi\u1ebft th\u00eam th\u00f4ng tin chi ti\u1ebft v\u1ec1 h\u1ecd</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Clip S\u1ed1ng c\u00f9ng World Cup 2018 s\u1ed1 33:</strong><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<iframe src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/IP6XzB7QfwY\" allow=\"autoplay; encrypted-media\" allowfullscreen=\"\" width=\"100%\" height=\"315\" frameborder=\"0\"></iframe> <br>\r\n<br>\r\nLuka Modric v\u00e0 Kylian Mbappe m\u1ed9t gi\u00e0, m\u1ed9t tr\u1ebb song \u0111\u1ec1u mang \u00e1o s\u1ed1 10 t\u1ea1i \u0110TQG v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec1u t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng r\u1ef1c r\u1ee1 t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018. \u1ede tu\u1ed5i 32, Modric v\u1eabn l\u00e0 \u201clinh h\u1ed3n\u201d \u1edf tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa c\u1ee7a Croatia. Anh di chuy\u1ec3n kh\u00f4ng ng\u1eebng ngh\u1ec9, cung c\u1ea5p ch\u1ea5t s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Balkan.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00f9ng v\u1edbi Croatia, Modric l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 ch\u1ecbu thua Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u1ea7y \u1eafp nh\u00e2n t\u00e0i. Trong l\u1ec5 trao gi\u1ea3i, M10 nh\u1eadn gi\u1ea3i th\u01b0\u1edfng x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng: Qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng v\u00e0ng gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u (C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t).<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong khi \u0111\u00f3, Mbappe m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 ra m\u1eaft th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi \u1edf m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i \u0111\u1ea7y ch\u1eefng ch\u1ea1c. 4 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0 th\u00e0nh t\u00edch r\u1ea5t \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng song v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a n\u00f3i l\u00ean h\u1ebft t\u1ea7m quan tr\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed3ng 19 tu\u1ed5i v\u1edbi Ph\u00e1p. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u1eefng b\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ea1y th\u1ea7n t\u1ed1c, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng x\u1eed l\u00fd nhanh nh\u1eb9n \u1edf ph\u1ea1m vi h\u1eb9p c\u1ee7a Mbappe lu\u00f4n khi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng chao \u0111\u1ea3o. Gi\u1ea3i th\u01b0\u1edfng C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t World Cup 2018 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh d\u1ea5u s\u1ef1 ra \u0111\u1eddi c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao s\u00e1ng t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Bongda24h.vn (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1386","checkdouble":"191520"},{"date":"16:23 18/07","title":"\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng nh\u00ed t\u00e1i hi\u1ec7n tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ecf","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/18/doi-bong-nhi-tai-hien-tran-chung-ket-world-cup-2018-tren-san-co.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 gi\u1eefa Ph\u00e1p v\u00e0 Croatia \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 nh\u00ed t\u00e1i hi\u1ec7n theo c\u00e1ch c\u1ef1c d\u1ec5 th\u01b0\u01a1ng.</h2><div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/hau-truong/tuyen-thu-nhat-ban-ket-hon-voi-vo-dien-vien-sau-world-cup-2018-188-191522.html\">Tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n k\u1ebft h\u00f4n v\u1edbi v\u1ee3 di\u1ec5n vi\u00ean sau World Cup 2018</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/song-cung-world-cup-2018-so-33-khong-phai-messi-day-la-2-nhan-to-m10-hay-nhat-the-gioi-421-191520.html\">S\u1ed1ng c\u00f9ng World Cup 2018 s\u1ed1 33: Kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i Messi, \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 2 nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 M10 hay nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/pho-tuong-tran-quoc-tuan-bat-ngo-rut-lui-khong-tranh-cu-chu-tich-vff-168-191519.html\">'Ph\u00f3 t\u01b0\u1edbng' Tr\u1ea7n Qu\u1ed1c Tu\u1ea5n b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd r\u00fat lui, kh\u00f4ng tranh c\u1eed Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch VFF</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/hau-truong/ngoi-sao-ronaldo-ban-moi-tai-san-o-tbn-188-191518.html\">Ng\u00f4i sao Ronaldo b\u00e1n m\u1ecdi t\u00e0i s\u1ea3n \u1edf TBN</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/tien-dung-thua-nhan-kho-canh-tranh-voi-van-lam-tai-asiad-2018-168-191517.html\">Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn kh\u00f3 c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1edbi \u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/world-cup-2018-qua-nhung-con-so-tieu-bieu-421-191516.html\">World Cup 2018 qua nh\u1eefng con s\u1ed1 ti\u00eau bi\u1ec3u</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1385","checkdouble":"191523"},{"date":"16:36 18/07","title":"Alisson \u1edf \u0111\u00e2u khi so s\u00e1nh v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/18/alisson-o-dau-khi-so-sanh-voi-nhung-thu-mon-hang-dau-ngoai-hang-anh.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chelsea mu\u1ed1n mua Alisson c\u1ee7a Roma trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p Courtois t\u1edbi Real, Liverpool c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n 26 tu\u1ed5i thay Karius. C\u00f9ng so s\u00e1nh nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 c\u1ee7a th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil so v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ea5y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nen liverpool 2\" title=\"N\u1ec1n liverpool 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/18/alisson-o-dau-khi-so-sanh-voi-nhung-thu-mon-hang-dau-ngoai-hang-anh.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>So s\u00e1nh nh\u1eefng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh v\u1edbi Alisson</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nLoris Karius (Liverpool)</h2>\r\n<p><strong>S\u1ed1 l\u1ea7n c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 \u1edf NHA m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua/90 ph\u00fat: 1.63</strong><strong><br>\r\nS\u1ed1 l\u1ea7n gi\u1eef s\u1ea1ch l\u01b0\u1edbi \u1edf NHA m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua: 10</strong><strong><br>\r\nT\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u1edf NHA m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua: 68.89%</strong><strong><br>\r\nS\u1ed1 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n (t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng) \u1edf NHA m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua/90 ph\u00fat: 27.42 (67.18%)</strong><strong><br>\r\nS\u1ed1 l\u1ed7i d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn b\u00e0n thua: 0</strong></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHLV Jurgen Klopp quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf Simon Mignolet v\u00e0 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng Loris Karius sau phong \u0111\u1ed9 thi\u1ebfu \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9. Khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c tr\u1ecdng d\u1ee5ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1993 \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chelsea mu\u1ed1n mua Alisson N\u00ean hay kh\u00f4ng n\u00ean h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chelsea mu\u1ed1n mua Alisson N\u00ean hay kh\u00f4ng n\u00ean h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/2/5/Chelsea-muon-mua-Alisson-Nen-hay-khong-nen-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea c\u1ee7a Karius \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i l\u00e0 kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede giai \u0111o\u1ea1n l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1, c\u00f3 th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m Karius gi\u1eef s\u1ea1ch l\u01b0\u1edbi 5/7 tr\u1eadn tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng. Phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a anh gi\u00fap The Kop c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 4 \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh v\u00e0 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft Champions League. Ch\u1ec9 ti\u1ebfc r\u1eb1ng trong tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft C1 2018 v\u1edbi Real c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 25 tu\u1ed5i l\u1ea1i c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u qu\u00e1 t\u1ec7.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nB\u1ecf qua nh\u1eefng sai l\u1ea7m trong tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft Champions League 2018, nh\u00ecn chung m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a Karius \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i l\u00e0 kh\u00e1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNg\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c gi\u1eef s\u1ea1ch l\u01b0\u1edbi 10/19 tr\u1eadn b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh. Karius ch\u1ec9 ch\u1ecbu tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m \u1edf 14/38 b\u00e0n thua m\u00e0 Liverpool ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn \u1edf Premier League 2017/18. N\u1ebfu \u0111\u1eb7t nh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea c\u1ee7a Karius b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh Alisson, ch\u00fang ta kh\u00f4ng th\u1ea5y s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t qu\u00e1 l\u1edbn.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKarius gi\u1eef s\u1ea1ch l\u01b0\u1edbi 53% s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u1edf NHA m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i, trong khi \u0111\u00f3 Alisson ch\u1ec9 gi\u1eef s\u1ea1ch l\u01b0\u1edbi 46% s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u1edf Serie A (17/37). V\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil nh\u1ec9nh h\u01a1n m\u1ed9t ch\u00fat (80,1% c\u1ee7a Alisson so v\u1edbi 68,98% c\u1ee7a Karius).</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1ec1 s\u1ed1 l\u1ed7i d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn b\u00e0n thua, Alisson l\u1ea1i v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i so v\u1edbi Karius (4 so v\u1edbi 0). Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n c\u1ee7a Liverpool c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 1,63 l\u1ea7n/90 ph\u00fat, th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Roma l\u00ean t\u1edbi 2,89 l\u1ea7n/90 ph\u00fat.</div>\r\n<h2>Jordan Pickford (Everton)</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>S\u1ed1 l\u1ea7n c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 \u1edf NHA m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua/90 ph\u00fat: 3.18</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>S\u1ed1 l\u1ea7n gi\u1eef s\u1ea1ch l\u01b0\u1edbi \u1edf NHA m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua: 10</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>T\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u1edf NHA m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua: 67.42%</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>S\u1ed1 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n (t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng) \u1edf NHA m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua/90 ph\u00fat: 25.46 (44.49%)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>S\u1ed1 l\u1ed7i d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn b\u00e0n thua: 5</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nEverton \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i b\u1ecf ra t\u1edbi 30 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Jordan Pickford t\u1eeb Sunderland, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1994 \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh khi h\u00f2a nh\u1eadp nhanh v\u00e0 ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Pickford khien doi khach khong the co ban thang\" title=\"Pickford khi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/11/11/MU-nham-thu-mon-Jordan-Pickford-thay-De-Gea-hinh-anh-2.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Pickford ch\u01a1i kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u00f9a v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i anh l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Goodison Park. Sau \u0111\u00f3 ng\u00f4i sao 24 tu\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng r\u1ef1c r\u1ee1 \u1edf World Cup 2018 khi gi\u00fap \u0110T Anh l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1edbi v\u00f2ng b\u00e1n k\u1ebft.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u1ede Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh 2017/18, Pickford c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 trung b\u00ecnh 3.18 l\u1ea7n/90 ph\u00fat, cao h\u01a1n m\u1ed9t ch\u00fat so v\u1edbi Alisson (2.89 l\u1ea7n/90 ph\u00fat). Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i 58 v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi nh\u1eb7t b\u00f3ng, cao h\u01a1n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u s\u1ed1 b\u00e0n thua m\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Roma (28).</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nT\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Pickford ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 67,42%, khi\u00eam t\u1ed1n h\u01a1n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u n\u1ebfu \u0111\u1eb7t c\u1ea1nh 80,1% c\u1ee7a Alisson. Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng chuy\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Pickford c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 chuy\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c c\u1ee7a anh ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 44,49%, k\u00e9m h\u01a1n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u con s\u1ed1 79,7% c\u1ee7a th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, Pickford cho th\u1ea5y kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ph\u00e1t b\u00f3ng d\u00e0i c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t, theo \u0111\u00f3 anh \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o ra 2 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i trong khi \u0111\u00f3 Alisson kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 c\u00fa ph\u00e1t b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o m\u1edf ra c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i.</div>\r\n<h2>Thibaut Courtois (Chelsea)</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>S\u1ed1 l\u1ea7n c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 \u1edf NHA m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua/90 ph\u00fat: 2.17</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>S\u1ed1 l\u1ea7n gi\u1eef s\u1ea1ch l\u01b0\u1edbi \u1edf NHA m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua: 15</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>T\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u1edf NHA m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua: 68.52%</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>S\u1ed1 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n (t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng) \u1edf NHA m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua/90 ph\u00fat: 28.09 (70.4%)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>S\u1ed1 l\u1ed7i d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn b\u00e0n thua: 1</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/chelsea-muon-dung-tien-de-bep-liverpool-vu-alisson-172-191489.html\" target=\"_blank\">Chelsea mu\u1ed1n mua Alisson</span>, h\u1ecd nh\u1eafm c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p Courtois t\u1edbi Real Madrid. Nh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea ch\u1ec9 ra r\u1eb1ng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed cho th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Thibaut Courtois\" title=\"Thibaut Courtois\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/7/thibaut-courtois-dua-ra-quyet-dinh-ve-tuong-lai.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Thibaut Courtois c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 nh\u01b0\u1eddng v\u1ecb tr\u00ed cho Alisson&nbsp;</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nCourtois b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh 35 l\u1ea7n \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh v\u00e0 nh\u1eadn 38 b\u00e0n thua, cao h\u01a1n so v\u1edbi con s\u1ed1 28 b\u00e0n thua sau 37 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Alisson. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 gi\u1eef s\u1ea1ch l\u01b0\u1edbi 15 tr\u1eadn \u1edf Premier League m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i, trong khi \u0111\u00f3 Alisson gi\u1eef s\u1ea1ch l\u01b0\u1edbi 17 tr\u1eadn \u1edf Serie A 2017/18.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 l\u00e0 c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t v\u1edbi 68,52%, song v\u1eabn th\u1ea5p h\u01a1n so v\u1edbi con s\u1ed1 80,1% c\u1ee7a th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Roma.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTh\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 duy nh\u1ea5t m\u00e0 Courtois \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n Alisson \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 s\u1ed1 l\u1ed7i d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn b\u00e0n thua. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, ng\u00f4i sao ch\u1ec9 m\u1eafc 1 l\u1ed7i d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn b\u00e0n thua, th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil b\u00ean ph\u00eda Roma l\u00e0 4.</div>\r\n<h2>Ederson (Man City)</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>S\u1ed1 l\u1ea7n c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 \u1edf NHA m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua/90 ph\u00fat: 1.63</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>S\u1ed1 l\u1ea7n gi\u1eef s\u1ea1ch l\u01b0\u1edbi \u1edf NHA m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua: 16</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>T\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u1edf NHA m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua: 68.29%</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>S\u1ed1 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n (t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng) \u1edf NHA m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua/90 ph\u00fat: 26.14 (85.34%)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>S\u1ed1 l\u1ed7i d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn b\u00e0n thua: 6</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nEderson \u0111ang l\u00e0 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n c\u00f3 gi\u00e1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng cao nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi, nh\u01b0ng trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0110T Brazil anh l\u1ea1i ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb cho Alisson. Nh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea c\u1ee7a hai th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n n\u00e0y \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t qu\u00e1 l\u1edbn.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"thu mon Ederson\" title=\"thu mon Ederson\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/14/Thu-mon-Ederson-gia-han-hop-dong-voi-Man-City--hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea c\u1ee7a Ederson kh\u00e1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng khi \u0111\u1eb7t c\u1ea1nh Alisson</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nEderson ra s\u00e2n 37 l\u1ea7n \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, b\u1eb1ng v\u1edbi s\u1ed1 l\u1ea7n thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a Alisson trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Roma \u1edf Serie A m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i. N\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n c\u1ee7a Man City gi\u1eef s\u1ea1ch l\u01b0\u1edbi 16 l\u1ea7n th\u00ec ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Roma gi\u1eef s\u1ea1ch l\u01b0\u1edbi 17 l\u1ea7n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nAlisson ch\u1ec9 ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn 27 b\u00e0n thua sau 37 tr\u1eadn, t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n m\u1ed9t ch\u00fat so v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u01b0\u01a1ng (28 b\u00e0n thua sau 37 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n). V\u1ec1 t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 chuy\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng, Ederson cho th\u1ea5y s\u1ef1 v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i so v\u1edbi Alisson (85,34% so v\u1edbi 79.7%).</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, vi\u1ec7c t\u1ef1 tin v\u00e0o kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng gi\u1eef b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e3 nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n b\u00e1o h\u1ea1i Ederson, theo \u0111\u00f3 anh c\u00f3 6 l\u1ea7n m\u1eafc l\u1ed7i d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn b\u00e0n thua, cao h\u01a1n 4 c\u1ee7a Alisson.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>David De Gea (MU)</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>S\u1ed1 l\u1ea7n c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 \u1edf NHA m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua/90 ph\u00fat: 3.11</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>S\u1ed1 l\u1ea7n gi\u1eef s\u1ea1ch l\u01b0\u1edbi \u1edf NHA m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua: 18</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>T\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u1edf NHA m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua: 80.28%</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>S\u1ed1 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n (t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng) \u1edf NHA m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua/90 ph\u00fat: 25.46 (57.54%)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>S\u1ed1 l\u1ed7i d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn b\u00e0n thua: 3</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nDavid de Gea l\u00e0 ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e2n c\u1ee7a danh hi\u1ec7u &ldquo;G\u0103ng tay v\u00e0ng&rdquo; Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 28 tu\u1ed5i c\u00f3 vinh d\u1ef1 nh\u1eadn danh hi\u1ec7u n\u00e0y. Trong s\u1ed1 nh\u1eefng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh, duy nh\u1ea5t De Gea cho th\u1ea5y s\u1ef1 v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i khi \u0111\u1eb7t c\u1ea1nh Alisson.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mourinho xac nhan De Gea bat chinh tai chung ket FA Cup\" title=\"Mourinho x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn De Gea b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh t\u1ea1i chung k\u1ebft FA Cup\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/19/diem-tin-bong-da-toi-146-mu-nhan-tin-cuc-mung-tu-real-madrid.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea c\u1ee7a De Gea v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i so v\u1edbi Alisson</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ee9 qua 90 ph\u00fat th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha l\u1ea1i c\u00f3 3.11 l\u1ea7n c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1, cao h\u01a1n m\u1ed9t ch\u00fat con s\u1ed1 2.89 c\u1ee7a th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil. C\u1ea3 De Gea v\u00e0 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n c\u1ee7a Roma \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 37 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n, ng\u00f4i sao 28 tu\u1ed5i gi\u1eef s\u1ea1ch l\u01b0\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n (18 so v\u1edbi 17).</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nT\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a De Gea l\u00ean t\u1edbi 80.28%, cao h\u01a1n m\u1ed9t ch\u00fat so v\u1edbi 80.1% c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i b\u00ean ph\u00eda Roma. Th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh c\u1ee7a M.U ch\u1ec9 m\u1eafc 3 l\u1ed7i d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn b\u00e0n thua, th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a Alisson l\u00e0 4.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTh\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 duy nh\u1ea5t m\u00e0 De Gea b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 th\u1ea5p h\u01a1n Alisson \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 chuy\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c (57.54% so v\u1edbi 79.7%), nh\u01b0ng \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 quan tr\u1ecdng b\u1edfi M.U d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi Mourinho kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng qu\u00e1 quan tr\u1ecdng \u0111\u1ebfn y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t b\u00f3ng.</div>\r\n<h2>Hugo Lloris (Tottenham)</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>S\u1ed1 l\u1ea7n c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 \u1edf NHA m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua/90 ph\u00fat: 2.39</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>S\u1ed1 l\u1ea7n gi\u1eef s\u1ea1ch l\u01b0\u1edbi \u1edf NHA m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua: 15</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>T\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u1edf NHA m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua: 70.09%</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>S\u1ed1 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n (t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng) \u1edf NHA m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua/90 ph\u00fat: 27.67 (75.2%)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>S\u1ed1 l\u1ed7i d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn b\u00e0n thua: 8</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHugo Lloris l\u00e0 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n s\u1ed1 1 c\u1ee7a Tottenham trong nh\u1eefng m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1986 \u0111\u00e3 duy tr\u00ec phong \u0111\u1ed9 kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Lloris phat bieu ve viec Real gianh ve vao Top 4 Ngoai hang Anh\" title=\"Lloris ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c Real gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 v\u00e0o Top 4 Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/10/hugo-lloris-vao-top-4-tot-hon-viec-gianh-1-danh-hieu.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Lloris gi\u1eef s\u1ea1ch l\u01b0\u1edbi 15 tr\u1eadn \u1edf NHA 2017/18</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p ra s\u00e2n 36 l\u1ea7n \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i v\u00e0 gi\u1eef s\u1ea1ch l\u01b0\u1edbi 15 l\u1ea7n, k\u00e9m 2 l\u1ea7n so v\u1edbi s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn gi\u1eef s\u1ea1ch l\u01b0\u1edbi c\u1ee7a Alisson \u1edf Roma. Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 c\u1ee7a Lloris c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 th\u1ea5p h\u01a1n m\u1ed9t ch\u00fat so v\u1edbi ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, Lloris c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 2.39 l\u1ea7n/90 ph\u00fat, t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng 70.09%, th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a Alisson l\u00e0 2.89 l\u1ea7n/90 ph\u00fat v\u00e0 t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng 80.1%. T\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1, t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 chuy\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c c\u1ee7a th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Spurs c\u0169ng th\u1ea5p h\u01a1n m\u1ed9t ch\u00fat (75,2% so v\u1edbi 78,9%).</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHugo Lloris \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 8 l\u1ea7n m\u1eafc l\u1ed7i d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn b\u00e0n thua \u1edf Premier League 2017/18, nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t trong s\u1ed1 nh\u1eefng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u1eb1m trong Top 5 Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh v\u00e0 g\u1ea5p \u0111\u00f4i so v\u1edbi Alisson.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n* Squawka.com</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1384","checkdouble":"191526"},{"date":"16:51 18/07","title":"3 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 c\u1ea7n Mourinho gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/18/3-van-de-can-mourinho-giai-quyet-o-mua-giai-201819.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>\u1ede m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i, Man United \u0111\u00e3 b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u bi\u1ebft c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ea1nh tranh trong top 6. Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Manchester l\u1ea1i r\u1ea5t hay s\u1ea3y ch\u00e2n khi ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 th\u1ea5p h\u01a1n. V\u00e0 sau \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 3 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 Mourinho c\u1ea7n s\u1eeda ch\u1eefa \u0111\u1ec3 h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Premier League 2018/19.</h2><h2>T\u00ecm m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u00e1nh ph\u1ea3i bi\u1ebft b\u00e1m bi\u00ean</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e2y c\u00f3 l\u1ebd l\u00e0 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ed3n t\u1ea1i t\u1eeb kh\u00e1 l\u00e2u c\u1ee7a Man United. K\u1ec3 t\u1eeb khi Antonio Valencia chuy\u1ec3n sang v\u1ecb tr\u00ed h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ph\u1ea3i, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf c\u0169ng m\u1ea5t \u0111i m\u1ed9t m\u1eabu ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh c\u1ed5 \u0111i\u1ec3n. H\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 k\u00e9o gi\u00e3n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 kh\u00f3 chia c\u1eaft \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4ng ng\u01b0\u1eddi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nJuan Mata l\u00e0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean hay \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ed1 tr\u00ed \u0111\u00e1 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ph\u1ea3i nh\u1ea5t m\u1ea5y n\u0103m qa. Nh\u01b0ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9. Xu h\u01b0\u1edbng thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a anh c\u0169ng l\u00e0 c\u1eaft v\u00e0o trung l\u1ed9 thay v\u00ec t\u1ea1t b\u00f3ng t\u1eeb ngo\u00e0i \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng bi\u00ean d\u1ecdc.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"3 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 c\u1ee7a MU c\u1ea7n Mourinho gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 201819 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"3 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 c\u1ee7a MU c\u1ea7n Mourinho gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 201819 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/1/17/3-van-de-cua-MU-can-Mourinho-giai-quyet-o-mua-giai-201819-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Man United \u0111ang thi\u1ebfu m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ph\u1ea3i bi\u1ebft b\u00e1m bi\u00ean</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u1eefng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u00e1nh \u0111ang l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o m\u1eaft xanh c\u1ee7a Man United l\u00fac n\u00e0y c\u00f3 Ivan Perisic v\u00e0 Hirving Lozano. C\u1ea3 hai c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec1u g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u1ea1nh t\u1ea1i <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018-c421-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">World Cup 2018</span> trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Croatia v\u00e0 Mexico.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nS\u1ef1 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a sao tr\u1ebb Andreas Pereira c\u0169ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1. Tuy v\u1eady, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ed1 tr\u00ed \u0111\u00e1 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 tr\u00e1i ho\u1eb7c ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng trung t\u00e2m. V\u1eady n\u00ean, Mourinho s\u1ebd l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u00e1ch gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 \u1edf h\u00e0nh lang ph\u1ea3i c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Manchester.</div>\r\n<h2>Chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 m\u1ed9t h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 tr\u00e1i h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Alex Sandro\" title=\"Alex Sandro\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/18/mu-tu-choi-mua-sao-khung-juventus-voi-gia-53-trieu-bang.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Alex Sandro \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c li\u00ean h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi Man United</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a Luke Shaw t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Old Trafford \u0111ang ng\u00e0n c\u00e2n treo s\u1ee3i t\u00f3c. Ashley Young \u0111\u00e3 b\u01b0\u1edbc sang tu\u1ed5i 33 v\u00e0 c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 m\u1edbi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 tr\u00e1i t\u1eeb m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc. Man United c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng hay m\u00e0 ph\u00f2ng th\u1ee7 c\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i th\u1eadt c\u1ea7n m\u1eabn.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nYoung l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p cho m\u1eb7t tr\u1eadn t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t. Nh\u01b0ng kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh v\u1eabn th\u01b0\u1eddng b\u1ecb nghi ng\u1edd. V\u00e0 Mourinho th\u00ec c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i v\u00e1 k\u00edn nh\u1eefng l\u1ed1i v\u00e0o khung th\u00e0nh c\u1ee7a De Gea n\u1ebfu mu\u1ed1n nh\u1eafm \u0111\u1ebfn ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Premier League theo l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nAlex Sandro l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o cho Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil c\u00f3 t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u1ea1t b\u00f3ng t\u1ed1t. Sandro \u0111ang l\u00e0 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thi\u1ebfu \u1edf Juventus. V\u1eady n\u00ean ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn anh c\u0169ng s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng g\u1eb7p v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 g\u00ec khi thi \u0111\u1ea5u cho m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng t\u1ea7m c\u1ee1 nh\u01b0 Man United.</div>\r\n<h2>Gi\u00fap Pogba v\u00e0 Martial ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Pogba Martial\" title=\"Pogba Martial\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/18/164824-3.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Pogba v\u00e0 Martial ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 phong \u0111\u1ed9 cao nh\u1ea5t trong nh\u1eefng m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 m\u00e0 Mourinho \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i tr\u0103n tr\u1edf su\u1ed1t hai m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua. Nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 bi\u1ebft r\u00f5 ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a Pogba. Nh\u01b0ng th\u01b0\u1eddng th\u00ec chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt m\u00e0 \u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0a ra kh\u00f4ng gi\u00fap Pogba c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a Pogba \u1edf World Cup 2018 ch\u1eafc h\u1eb3n s\u1ebd khi\u1ebfn Mourinho ph\u1ea3i ch\u00fa \u00fd. C\u00e1ch b\u1ed1 tr\u00ed \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p c\u0169ng kh\u00e1 gi\u1ed1ng Man United. V\u1edbi Matic v\u00e0 t\u00e2n binh Fred h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3, Pogba s\u1ebd c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ea5t di\u1ec5n h\u01a1n. N\u1ebfu m\u00f9a sau, Pogba c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u00e1i hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1edf World Cup, v\u1ecb th\u1ebf c\u1ee7a anh t\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u00e2ng cao.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong khi \u0111\u00f3, Martial \u0111ang d\u1ea7n b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ea9y kh\u1ecfi \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh sau khi Alexis Sanchez c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Old Trafford. Ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n c\u1ee7a Martial l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn v\u00e0 s\u1ebd th\u1eadt ti\u1ebfc n\u1ebfu anh l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn r\u1eddi kh\u1ecfi Man United v\u00e0o th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nMartial c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng trong vai tr\u00f2 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ho\u1eb7c ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 tr\u00e1i. V\u00e0 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 \u0111au \u0111\u1ea7u d\u00e0nh cho Mourinho l\u00e0 Martial s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea1nh tranh kh\u1ed1c li\u1ec7t v\u1edbi Alexis Sanchez c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 Marcus Rashford cho m\u1ed9t su\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Man United:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mu-se-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-gareth-bale-neu-172-191511.html\">MU s\u1ebd chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Gareth Bale n\u1ebfu...</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mu-lam-dieu-nay-de-chieu-mo-bang-duoc-ivan-perisic-172-191494.html\">MU l\u00e0m \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Ivan Perisic</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1383","checkdouble":"191528"},{"date":"17:13 18/07","title":"Quy\u1ebft theo nghi\u1ec7p HLV, Henry nh\u1eadn l\u1eddi c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o t\u1eeb th\u1ea7y Wenger","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/15/quyet-theo-nghiep-hlv-henry-nhan-loi-canh-bao-tu-thay-wenger.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Arsene Wenger kh\u00f4ng nghi ng\u1edd t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u0169, nh\u01b0ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Thierry Henry s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i hy sinh, \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ed5i r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u nh\u01b0 \u00f4ng m\u1ed9t khi \u0111\u00e3 d\u1ea5n th\u00e2n v\u00e0o con \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n.</h2><div>B\u1ec9 k\u1ebft th\u00fac k\u1ef3 World Cup 2018 v\u1edbi t\u1ea5m huy ch\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed3ng, th\u00e0nh t\u00edch cao nh\u1ea5t trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 n\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u00e0. Chi\u1ebfn c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0110\u1ecf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u00f3p c\u00f4ng l\u1edbn b\u1edfi c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u00f4i sao thu\u1ed9c \"th\u1ebf h\u1ec7 v\u00e0ng, nh\u01b0ng t\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ng\u00f3 l\u01a1 vai tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a ban hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n, t\u1eeb HLV Roberto Martinez \u0111\u1ebfn tr\u1ee3 l\u00fd Thierry Henry.</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Gi\u00e1o S\u01b0 Wenger c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o Henry khi l\u00e0m HLV chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Gi\u00e1o S\u01b0 Wenger c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o Henry khi l\u00e0m HLV chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/15/quyet-theo-nghiep-hlv-henry-nhan-loi-canh-bao-tu-thay-wenger.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Wenger c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o Henry khi l\u00e0m HLV\u00a0</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">V\u1edbi vai tr\u00f2 nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ecbnh mang \u0111\u1ebfn th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng cho \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n B\u1ec9, Henry c\u00e0ng t\u1ef1 tin d\u1ea5n th\u00e2n v\u00e0o con \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n sau hai n\u0103m h\u1ecdc vi\u1ec7c cho Martinez. M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e0i Sky Sports l\u00e0m c\u00f4ng t\u00e1c b\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1eadp trung v\u00e0o ngh\u1ec1 tay ph\u1ea3i.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div><br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, tham v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a Henry c\u0169ng nh\u1eadn s\u1ef1 c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o t\u1eeb \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u01b0\u01a1ng Arsene Wenger, khi Gi\u00e1o S\u01b0 b\u1ed9c b\u1ea1ch nh\u1eefng kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n trong ngh\u1ec1 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Chia s\u1ebb c\u1ee7a c\u1ef1u chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia m\u1edbi chia tay Arsenal sau 22 n\u0103m g\u1eafn b\u00f3:</div>\r\n<div><br>\r\n\"T\u00f4i h\u1ed1i ti\u1ebfc v\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i hy sinh r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u th\u1ee9 v\u00ec c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed khi\u1ebfn nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi xunh quanh c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng, trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 ch\u00ednh gia \u0111\u00ecnh. T\u00f4i khi\u1ebfn cho h\u1ecd bu\u1ed3n ch\u00e1n, ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng t\u00f4i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t g\u00e3 \u0111\u00e0n \u00f4ng \u00edch k\u1ef7 v\u00e0 ch\u1eb3ng bi\u1ebft quan t\u00e2m \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec h\u1ebft ngo\u00e0i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1.\"</div>\r\n<div><br>\r\n\"T\u00f4i th\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ecfi r\u1eb1ng li\u1ec7u Thierry Henry hay Patrick Vieira c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng HLV gi\u1ecfi hay kh\u00f4ng, v\u00e0 c\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi lu\u00f4n lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 c\u00f3. H\u1ecd th\u00f4ng minh, s\u1edf h\u1eefu \u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7 ph\u1ea9m ch\u1ea5t v\u00e0 th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 th\u1ea5u hi\u1ec3u b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, nh\u01b0ng li\u1ec7u h\u1ecd c\u00f3 d\u00e1m ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn hy sinh, \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ed5i nhi\u1ec1u th\u1ee9 kh\u00f4ng m\u1ed9t khi \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u00e1m \u1ea3nh c\u1ea3 trong gi\u1ea5c ng\u1ee7?\"</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/dt-bi-gianh-hang-ba-world-cup-cho-nhe-euro-2020-421-191212.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/15/dt-bi-gianh-hang-ba-world-cup-cho-nhe-euro-2020.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/dt-bi-gianh-hang-ba-world-cup-cho-nhe-euro-2020-421-191212.html\">\u0110T B\u1ec9 gi\u00e0nh h\u1ea1ng Ba World Cup: Ch\u1edd nh\u00e9 EURO 2020!</span><br>\r\n\u1ede tr\u1eadn tranh h\u1ea1ng Ba World Cup n\u0103m nay, \u0110T B\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e3 tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n m\u1ed9t l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i s\u1eafc n\u00e9t v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng k\u00e9m ph\u1ea7n hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc d\u00e0n sao c\u1ee7a \u0110T Anh. V\u00e0 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c duy tr\u00ec \u0111i\u1ec1u...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1382","checkdouble":"191531"},{"date":"17:38 18/07","title":"3 l\u00fd do tin t\u01b0\u1edfng Real Madrid s\u1ebd chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Eden Hazard","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/18/3-ly-do-tin-tuong-real-madrid-se-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-eden-hazard.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Real Madrid mu\u1ed1n mua Eden Hazard thay th\u1ebf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed do Ronaldo \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i, d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 3 l\u00fd do tin t\u01b0\u1edfng Los Blancos s\u1ebd chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">S\u1ef1 quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m c\u1ee7a Real Madrid</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong nh\u1eefng m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, Real Madrid mu\u1ed1n mua Eden Hazard. Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Florentino Perez r\u1ea5t th\u00edch phong c\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 v\u00e0 r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1991 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t \u1edf s\u00e2n Bernabeu.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Real Madrid mu\u1ed1n mua Eden Hazard 3 l\u00fd do tin Real s\u1ebd th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Real Madrid mu\u1ed1n mua Eden Hazard 3 l\u00fd do tin Real s\u1ebd th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/18/ha.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Real mu\u1ed1n mua b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Eden Hazard</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/chinh-thuc-real-xac-nhan-ronaldo-cap-ben-juventus-180-190888.html\" target=\"_blank\">Cristiano Ronaldo c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Juventus</span>, s\u1ef1 ra \u0111i c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i kho\u1ea3ng tr\u1ed1ng m\u00eanh m\u00f4ng n\u01a1i h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Los Blancos. Nh\u01b0 v\u1eady l\u00e0 2 k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Bernabeu \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1ea5t nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nH\u00e8 n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i, K\u1ec1n k\u1ec1n tr\u1eafng b\u00e1n Alvaro Morata cho Chelsea v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 70 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, ngo\u00e0i ra h\u1ecd c\u00f2n \u0111\u1ec3 James Rodriguez t\u1edbi Bayern Munich theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n c\u00f3 th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n 2 n\u0103m. H\u00e8 n\u0103m nay, Real ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c m\u1ea5t Ronaldo v\u00e0o tay Juventus.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1ec3 qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u ng\u00f4i sao t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng ra \u0111i, NHM Real \u0111ang g\u00e2y \u00e1p l\u1ef1c bu\u1ed9c BL\u0110 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao l\u1edbn tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMbappe v\u00e0 Neymar l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Los Blancos nh\u1eafm t\u1edbi, song m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 m\u00e0 PSG \u0111\u01b0a ra khi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Bernabeu kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nPSG \u0111\u00f2i 400 tri\u1ec7u euro cho Neymar v\u00e0 290 tri\u1ec7u euro cho Mbappe, Real kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u1ecd s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n n\u00e0y. Los Blancos s\u1ebd d\u1ed3n to\u00e0n l\u1ef1c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Eden Hazard c\u1ee7a Chelsea \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u1ec1u l\u00f2ng NHM.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTheo Daily Mail, Real mua Hazard v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 150 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, h\u1ecd \u0111ang l\u00e0m m\u1ecdi c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Hazard mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Real Madrid</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau tr\u1eadn thua 0-1 c\u1ee7a B\u1ec9 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p \u1edf b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018, khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ecfi v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Eden Hazard \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn NHM Chelsea lo l\u1eafng khi kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chia tay Stamford Bridge sau 6 n\u0103m g\u1eafn b\u00f3.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Sarri muon bien Hazard thanh trung tam trong loi choi cua Chelsea\" title=\"Sarri mu\u1ed1n bi\u1ebfn Hazard th\u00e0nh trung t\u00e2m trong l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a Chelsea\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/13/muon-thanh-cong-hlv-sarri-can-phai-ban-eden-hazard.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Hazard mu\u1ed1n t\u1edbi Real \u1edf H\u00e8 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 6 n\u0103m g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi Chelsea, t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng k\u1ef7 ni\u1ec7m \u0111\u1eb9p \u1edf Stamford Bridge. T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u l\u1edbn c\u00f9ng Chelsea, t\u00f4i \u0111ang suy ngh\u0129 nghi\u00eam t\u00fac v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c c\u00f3 n\u00ean r\u1eddi Chelsea \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 hay kh\u00f4ng&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&ldquo;S\u1ebd c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n nh\u1eefng th\u1eed th\u00e1ch m\u1edbi trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p, t\u00f4i s\u1ebd c\u00e2n nh\u1eafc k\u1ef9 l\u01b0\u1ee1ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi \u0111\u01b0a ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng. T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o nhi\u1ec1u y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKhi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ecfi v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c Real Madrid quan t\u00e2m m\u00ecnh, Hazard ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c: &ldquo;H\u1ecd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng CLB v\u0129 \u0111\u1ea1i nh\u1ea5t ch\u00e2u \u00c2u, h\u1ecd lu\u00f4n duy tr\u00ec tham v\u1ecdng r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn. B\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 ng\u00f4i sao l\u1edbn n\u00e0o c\u0169ng mong \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Real Madrid&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi nh\u1eefng ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u c\u1ee7a Eden Hazard, d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 anh \u0111\u00e3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb t\u00e2m l\u00fd \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Bernabeu \u1edf H\u00e8 2018. Real \u0111ang chi\u1ebfm tr\u1ecdn tr\u00e1i tim c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9, v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 c\u1ee7a Los Blancos ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n gi\u00e1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi Chelsea m\u00e0 th\u00f4i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Chelsea g\u1eb7p \u00e1p l\u1ef1c ph\u1ea3i b\u00e1n Hazard</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a Eden Hazard v\u1edbi Chelsea ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ebfn H\u00e8 2020, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London \u0111\u00e3 nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi nh\u01b0ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1991 \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i. N\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng nhanh ch\u00f3ng b\u00e1n ng\u00f4i sao 27 tu\u1ed5i \u1edf H\u00e8 2018, Chelsea c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u1ecb Real \u00e9p gi\u00e1 v\u00e0o H\u00e8 n\u0103m t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Eden Hazard Chelsea\" title=\"Eden Hazard Chelsea\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/31/chelsea-tu-choi-loi-de-nghi-dau-tien-cua-real-cho-hazard.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Chelsea c\u1ea7n nhanh ch\u00f3ng gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Eden Hazard&nbsp;</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede \u0111\u1ed9 tu\u1ed5i 27, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 \u0111ang b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o giai \u0111o\u1ea1n ch\u00edn nh\u1ea5t trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p. T\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a Hazard r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n th\u00eam l\u00ean m\u1ed9t t\u1ea7m cao m\u1edbi v\u00e0 nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u1ebfu Chelsea bu\u1ed9c l\u00f2ng ph\u1ea3i b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y th\u00ec \u1edf m\u00f9a H\u00e8 2018 l\u00e0 giai \u0111o\u1ea1n th\u00edch h\u1ee3p nh\u1ea5t.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nS\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n 150 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng m\u00e0 Real Madrid d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ecbnh chi ra \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 h\u1ee3p l\u00fd, v\u1edbi kho\u1ea3n ng\u00e2n s\u00e1ch kh\u1ed5ng l\u1ed3 thu v\u1ec1 t\u1eeb vi\u1ec7c b\u00e1n Hazard, HLV Sarri c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nGareth Bale (Real Madrid), Leon Bailey (Bayer Leverkusen) v\u00e0 Anthony Martial \u0111ang l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eafm thay Hazard, \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u00e0i n\u0103ng h\u1ecd ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed do c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTheo quy \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u1edbi, 48 gi\u1edd tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh 2018/19 kh\u1edfi tranh nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u cao nh\u1ea5t x\u1ee9 s\u1edf s\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00f9 s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p mua th\u00eam c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7. T\u1eeb nay \u0111\u1ebfn th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u00f3 ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n kho\u1ea3ng 20 ng\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nChelsea c\u1ea7n nhanh ch\u00f3ng d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Hazard. N\u1ebfu anh \u1edf l\u1ea1i th\u00ec kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec \u0111\u1ec3 n\u00f3i, nh\u01b0ng n\u1ebfu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 27 tu\u1ed5i quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m ra \u0111i, The Blues c\u1ea7n nhanh ch\u00f3ng b\u00e1n anh \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 thay th\u1ebf, qua \u0111\u00f3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t cho m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London hi\u1ec3u \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 th\u1eddi gian t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1eafng nghe nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb, tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi s\u1edbm b\u1eaft tay v\u00e0o vi\u1ec7c t\u00ecm ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 27 tu\u1ed5i. \u00c1p l\u1ef1c v\u1ec1 th\u1eddi gian c\u1ee7a Chelsea ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ec3 Real th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 bom t\u1ea5n n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1381","checkdouble":"191533"},{"date":"17:46 18/07","title":"G\u00f3c Real Madrid: 4 c\u00e1i t\u00ean h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u1ee3i nh\u1ea5t d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi Lopetegui","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/15/goc-real-madrid-4-cai-ten-huong-loi-nhat-duoi-thoi-lopetegui.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Sau s\u1ef1 ra \u0111i c\u1ee7a Zidane, Julen Lopetegui \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c ti\u1ebfp qu\u1ea3n K\u1ec1n k\u1ec1n tr\u1eafng. v\u00e0 d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trao nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u1edf Real Madrid c\u1ee7a HLV Lopetegui.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nGareth Bale<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ng\u00f4i sao s\u00e1ng nh\u1ea5t Bernabeu &ndash; Cris Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c gia nh\u1eadp Juventus v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 100 tri\u1ec7u euro. V\u00e0 cho d\u00f9 vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n gi\u1eefa Bale vs Lopetegui v\u1eabn \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ti\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh, nh\u01b0ng c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn HLV T\u00e2y Ban Nha mu\u1ed1n gi\u1eef ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi x\u1ee9 Wales \u1edf l\u1ea1i. \u00d4ng t\u1ef1 tin c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap Bale l\u1ea5y l\u1ea1i phong \u0111\u1ed9 cao nh\u1ea5t.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Gareth Bale \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 26 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n t\u1ea1i La Liga \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p 16 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. B\u1ecb gi\u00e1n \u0111o\u1ea1n b\u1edfi nh\u1eefng ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u, Bale kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Real. Nh\u01b0ng trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y v\u00e0o s\u00e2n t\u1eeb b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb v\u00e0 g\u00f3p 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c Liverpool.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Real Madrid c\u1ee7a HLV Lopetegui 4 c\u00e1i t\u00ean d\u1ef1 b\u00e1o t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Real Madrid c\u1ee7a HLV Lopetegui 4 c\u00e1i t\u00ean d\u1ef1 b\u00e1o t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/14/Real-Madrid-cua-HLV-Lopetegui-4-cai-ten-du-bao-toa-sang-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Gareth Bale s\u1ebd \u0111\u00f3ng vai tr\u00f2 quan tr\u1ecdng h\u01a1n</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau s\u1ef1 ra \u0111i c\u1ee7a CR7, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn Los Blancos kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u00e1nh m\u1ea5t ng\u00f4i sao kh\u1ea3 d\u0129 c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh &ndash; khi nh\u1eefng Neymar, Mbappe hay Hazard c\u00f2n qu\u00e1 xa v\u1eddi (v\u00e0 c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ebfn c\u0169ng m\u1ea5t th\u1eddi gian h\u00f2a nh\u1eadp). B\u1edfi v\u1eady, Gareth Bale s\u1ebd nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i thi \u0111\u1ea5u h\u01a1n, v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin c\u1ee7a anh s\u1ebd tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra n\u1ebfu Bale ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn \u1edf l\u1ea1i Bernabeu, thay v\u00ec \u0111i theo ti\u1ebfng g\u1ecdi c\u1ee7a Man United. \u0110\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi, \u0111i\u1ec1u quan tr\u1ecdng l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i l\u1ea5y l\u1ea1i th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mu-se-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-gareth-bale-neu-172-191511.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/1/mu-se-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-gareth-bale-neu.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mu-se-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-gareth-bale-neu-172-191511.html\">MU s\u1ebd chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Gareth Bale n\u1ebfu...</span><br>\r\nMU mu\u1ed1n mua Gareth Bale t\u1eeb Real Madrid, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf v\u1eabn c\u00f2n c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi x\u1ee9 Wales n\u1ebfu Los Blancos quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh mua m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Dani Ceballos<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 ti\u1ec3u Iniesta c\u1ee7a T\u00e2y Ban Nha, nh\u01b0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 sinh n\u0103m 1996 hi\u1ebfm khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Real Madrid. T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, anh kh\u00f3 l\u00f2ng c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng Casemiro, Toni Kroos v\u00e0 Luka Modric. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng b\u1eb1ng Mateo Kovacic trong danh s\u00e1ch d\u1ef1 ph\u00f2ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u01b0ng \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi Julen Lopetegui, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t \u01b0a th\u00edch phong c\u00e1ch thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a Ceballos. Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 tr\u1ebb tu\u1ed5i c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t nh\u1ecbp \u0111\u1ed9 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t. Trong 6 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n t\u1ea1i m\u00e0u \u00e1o U12 T\u00e2y Ban Nha, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 4 b\u00e0n &ndash; v\u00e0 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd l\u00e0 qu\u00e2n b\u00e0i quan tr\u1ecdng trong m\u1ecdi k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch c\u1ee7a t\u00e2n thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng Real Madrid.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ceballos\" title=\"Ceballos\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/18/ceba.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ceballos s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<h2>Marco Asensio<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ng\u00f4i sao m\u1edbi n\u1ed5i c\u1ee7a K\u1ec1n k\u1ec1n tr\u1eafng \u0111\u00e3 tham d\u1ef1 32 tr\u1eadn La Liga m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc, ghi 6 b\u00e0n v\u00e0 c\u00f3 6 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o, d\u00f9 h\u1ea7u h\u1ebft th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u00e0o s\u00e2n t\u1eeb b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb. V\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u C\u0110V Real, Marco Asensio \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1eeba k\u1ebf c\u1ee7a Cris Ronaldo. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u00fat ph\u1ea1t, chuy\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng, ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o, x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i v\u00e0 r\u00ea d\u1eaft \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 b\u1ecf qua tuy\u1ec7t chi\u00eau \u0111\u00e1ng s\u1ee3 nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Asensio &ndash; nh\u1eefng c\u00fa s\u00fat xa b\u1eb1ng l\u00f2ng trong, t\u1ea1o n\u00ean nh\u1eefng si\u00eau ph\u1ea9m \u0111\u00e1ng kinh ng\u1ea1c. C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y ch\u1eb3ng thi\u1ebfu \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao xu\u1ea5t ch\u00fang trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai, n\u1ebfu anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ea1o \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n ra s\u00e2n h\u00e0ng tu\u1ea7n.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, HLV Zidane th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng Asensio nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t qu\u00e2n b\u00e0i chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c trong hi\u1ec7p 2, v\u00e0 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y c\u1ee9u r\u1ed7i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng &ndash; ti\u00eau bi\u1ec3u nh\u01b0 tr\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft Champions League v\u1edbi H\u00f9m x\u00e1m Bayern. V\u1edbi th\u00f3i quen \u01b0a d\u00f9ng nh\u1eefng t\u00e0i n\u0103ng tr\u1ebb, Asensio s\u1ebd c\u00f3 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai t\u01b0\u01a1i s\u00e1ng d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi HLV Lopetegui.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"tien ve Asensio\" title=\"tien ve Asensio\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/9/12/asensio-thua-nhan-kha-nang-roi-real-madrid.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Asensio r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng v\u1edbi Real Madrid c\u1ee7a HLV Lopetegui</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<h2>James Rodriguez<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00e1i t\u00ean c\u00f3 l\u1ebd l\u00e0 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd nh\u1ea5t v\u1edbi c\u1ea3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 Real Madrid. Nh\u01b0ng theo nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e1o ch\u00ed T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/james-rodriguez-co-the-tro-lai-real-ngay-mua-he-nay-180-191502.html\" target=\"_blank\">ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 James Rodriguez tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Bernabeu l\u00e0 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra</span>. Anh v\u00e0 HLV Lopetegui \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 bu\u1ed5i tr\u00f2 chuy\u1ec7n v\u1edbi nhau c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y 2 tu\u1ea7n v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i, d\u00f9 James v\u1eabn \u0111ang c\u00f2n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n v\u1edbi Bayern Munich.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o v\u1edbi s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3, phong c\u00e1ch chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt c\u1ee7a Julen Lopetegui, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Colombia ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ea5t di\u1ec5n n\u1ebfu anh quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169. Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o, chuy\u1ec1n d\u00e0i, s\u00fat xa c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1991 v\u1eabn c\u00f2n r\u1ea5t h\u1eefu d\u1ee5ng, h\u01a1n n\u1eefa anh c\u00f3 t\u00ecnh y\u00eau r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn v\u1edbi Real Madrid &ndash; v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 r\u1eddi \u0111i khi kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Zidane tin t\u01b0\u1edfng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"James Rodriguez se chong lai doi bong cu cua minh\" title=\"James Rodriguez s\u1ebd ch\u1ed1ng l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/25/james-rodriguez-co-the-tro-lai-real-ngay-mua-he-nay.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>James Rodriguez s\u1ebd tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169?</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u00f3 th\u1ec3 xem James l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t phi\u00ean b\u1ea3n c\u1ee7a Asensio gi\u00e0u kinh nghi\u1ec7m h\u01a1n. C\u00f9ng v\u1edbi Isco, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Colombia ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd \u0111\u00f3ng vai tr\u00f2 quan tr\u1ecdng trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o K\u1ec1n k\u1ec1n tr\u1eafng, n\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Ho\u00e0ng gia T\u00e2y Ban Nha kh\u00f4ng chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00eam b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 ng\u00f4i sao bom t\u1ea5n n\u00e0o trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/3-ly-do-tin-tuong-real-madrid-se-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-eden-hazard-172-191533.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/18/3-ly-do-tin-tuong-real-madrid-se-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-eden-hazard.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/3-ly-do-tin-tuong-real-madrid-se-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-eden-hazard-172-191533.html\">3 l\u00fd do tin t\u01b0\u1edfng Real Madrid s\u1ebd chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Eden Hazard</span><br>\r\nReal Madrid mu\u1ed1n mua Eden Hazard thay th\u1ebf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed do Ronaldo \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i, d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 3 l\u00fd do tin t\u01b0\u1edfng Los Blancos s\u1ebd chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/real-madrid-se-song-tot-ma-khong-can-cristiano-ronaldo-421-191509.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/17/real-madrid-se-song-tot-ma-khong-can-cristiano-ronaldo.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/real-madrid-se-song-tot-ma-khong-can-cristiano-ronaldo-421-191509.html\">Real Madrid s\u1ebd s\u1ed1ng t\u1ed1t m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n Cristiano Ronaldo</span><br>\r\nC\u1ef1u danh th\u1ee7 Antonio Cassano ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 khi si\u00eau sao Cristiano Ronaldo ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c gia nh\u1eadp Juventus t\u1eeb Real Madrid trong k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/zidane-sap-tai-ngo-ronaldo-tai-juve-176-191479.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2016/1/7/HLV-Zidane-noi-gi-ve-tuong-lai-Ronaldo-hinh-anh-2.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/zidane-sap-tai-ngo-ronaldo-tai-juve-176-191479.html\">N\u00d3NG: HLV Zidane s\u1eafp t\u00e1i ng\u1ed9 Ronaldo t\u1ea1i Juventus</span><br>\r\nTheo ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng T\u00e2y Ban Nha, HLV Zidane c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c sau khi chia tay Real Madrid. V\u00e0 b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 ti\u1ebfp theo c\u1ee7a Zizou s\u1ebd l\u00e0 CLB...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1380","checkdouble":"191534"},{"date":"10:26 18/07","title":"Sao tuy\u1ec3n Anh s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chia tay Chelsea n\u1ebfu \u00edt \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/24/chelsea-san-sang-chia-tay-cahill.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Sau m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea7y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng, trung v\u1ec7 Gary Cahill \u0111ang s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chia tay Chelsea \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n thi \u0111\u1ea5u nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n.</h2><h2>Gary Cahill\u00a0s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chia tay Chelsea</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Gary Cahill s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chia tay Chelsea h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Gary Cahill s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chia tay Chelsea h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/24/chelsea-san-sang-chia-tay-cahill.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Trung v\u1ec7 Gary Cahill s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chia tay Chelsea n\u1ebfu \u00edt \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">Gia nh\u1eadp \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge t\u1eeb Bolton v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 7 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng Anh \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u0103m 2012, trung v\u1ec7 Gary Cahill \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng n\u0103m th\u00e1ng h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac t\u1ea1i Chelsea.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, khi m\u00e0 th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c v\u00e0 phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u0111\u00e3 suy gi\u1ea3m v\u00ec l\u00fd do tu\u1ed5i t\u00e1c, Cahill \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n l\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1ea1i Chelsea. Anh ch\u1ec9 ra s\u00e2n t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 27 tr\u1eadn t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh, trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n v\u00e0o s\u00e2n t\u1eeb b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i, Cahill c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n khi ph\u1ea3i th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean l\u00e0m b\u1ea1n v\u1edbi b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb. \u201cS\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 d\u1ec5 ch\u1ecbu khi b\u1ea1n ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i ngo\u00e0i nh\u1eefng cu\u1ed9c ch\u01a1i l\u1edbn v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u. Nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi cho r\u1eb1ng khi b\u1ea1n l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00ec b\u1ea1n v\u1eabn c\u00f3 t\u1ea7m \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng trong ph\u00f2ng thay \u0111\u1ed3 song th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i nh\u01b0 v\u1eady\u201d.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00ec l\u00fd do \u0111\u00f3, Gary Cahill c\u0169ng \u0111ang t\u00ednh t\u1edbi chuy\u1ec7n ra \u0111i \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y. Theo t\u1edd Evening Standard, trong th\u1eddi gian t\u1edbi trung v\u1ec7 \u0110T Anh s\u1ebd c\u00f3 cu\u1ed9c th\u1ea3o lu\u1eadn v\u1edbi t\u00e2n HLV Sarri \u0111\u1ec3 n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 vai tr\u00f2 v\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ra s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u1edf m\u00f9a b\u00f3ng m\u1edbi. N\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ea1t k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng, trung v\u1ec7 32 tu\u1ed5i n\u00e0y s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chia tay Chelsea \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede chi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, HLV Sarri c\u0169ng \u0111ang s\u1ed1t s\u1eafng b\u1ed5 sung m\u1ed9t g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t m\u1edbi cho h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 The Blues. V\u00e0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ef1u HLV Napoli nh\u1eafm \u0111\u1ebfn l\u00e0 Daniele Rugani. Kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng trung v\u1ec7 \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh \u1edf Juve, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Chelsea c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Rugani l\u00e0 kh\u00e1 cao. Trong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9, Rugani c\u0169ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u01b0ng c\u1ee7a HLV Sarri khi hai ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f2n l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c chung \u1edf Empoli.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/hlv-conte-sap-ve-ac-milan-sau-khi-chia-tay-chelsea-172-191485.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/19/hlv-conte-sap-ve-ac-milan-sau-khi-chia-tay-chelsea.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/hlv-conte-sap-ve-ac-milan-sau-khi-chia-tay-chelsea-172-191485.html\">HLV Conte s\u1eafp c\u00f3 b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi sau khi chia tay Chelsea</span><br>\r\nTheo b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi \u00dd, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n Antonio Conte \u0111\u00e3 t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho m\u00ecnh b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi sau khi b\u1ecb CLB Chelsea sa th\u1ea3i c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y ch\u01b0a l\u00e2u.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/hlv-bi-ung-ho-hazard-bo-chelsea-sang-real-madrid-172-191484.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/15/hlv-bi-ung-ho-hazard-bo-chelsea-sang-real-madrid.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/hlv-bi-ung-ho-hazard-bo-chelsea-sang-real-madrid-172-191484.html\">HLV B\u1ec9 \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 Hazard b\u1ecf Chelsea sang Real Madrid</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-muon-tai-ngo-petr-cech-172-191487.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/5/chelsea-muon-tai-ngo-petr-cech.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-muon-tai-ngo-petr-cech-172-191487.html\">Chelsea mu\u1ed1n t\u00e1i ng\u1ed9 ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u0169 t\u1eeb Arsenal</span><br>\r\nTheo ngu\u1ed3n tin t\u1eeb t\u1edd Daily Mail, CLB Chelsea \u0111ang c\u00f3 \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 l\u1ea1i th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh k\u1ef3 c\u1ef1u Petr Cech tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi kh\u1edfi tranh.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/hlv-sarri-nai-ni-nhung-tru-cot-o-lai-chelsea-172-191488.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/19/hlv-sarri-nai-ni-nhung-tru-cot-o-lai-chelsea.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/hlv-sarri-nai-ni-nhung-tru-cot-o-lai-chelsea-172-191488.html\">HLV Sarri n\u00e0i n\u1ec9 nh\u1eefng tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t \u1edf l\u1ea1i Chelsea</span><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Chelsea m\u00f9a t\u1edbi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 m\u1ea5t r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao l\u1edbn, t\u00e2n HLV Maurizio Sarri \u0111ang l\u00e0m m\u1ecdi c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u0103n c\u1ea3n \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 x\u1ea3y ra.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1379","checkdouble":"191493"},{"date":"10:19 18/07","title":"MU l\u00e0m \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Ivan Perisic","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/14/mu-lam-dieu-nay-de-chieu-mo-bang-duoc-ivan-perisic.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>MU mu\u1ed1n mua Ivan Perisic c\u1ee7a Inter Milan, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Old Trafford d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ecbnh chi \u0111\u1ee7 62 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng nh\u01b0 ph\u00eda \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Italia y\u00eau c\u1ea7u.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Mourinho th\u00e8m kh\u00e1t Ivan Perisic</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMourinho \u0111ang r\u1ea5t c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p. V\u1ecb tr\u00ed n\u00e0y \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua do Juan Mata \u0111\u1ea3m nhi\u1ec7m song ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e1 tr\u00f2n vai, anh ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u00f9ng 3 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chi 62 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, MU mu\u1ed1n mua Ivan Perisic \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chi 62 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, MU mu\u1ed1n mua Ivan Perisic \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/14/mu-lam-dieu-nay-de-chieu-mo-bang-duoc-ivan-perisic.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Mourinho r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n MU mua Perisic</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00e1nh tr\u00e1i M.U c\u00f3 3 c\u00e1i t\u00ean \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 Sanchez, Martial v\u00e0 Rashford. Tuy nhi\u00ean, c\u00e1nh ph\u1ea3i l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn qu\u00e1 t\u1ed1t. Mourinho mu\u1ed1n MU mua b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh ph\u1ea3i \u1edf \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p cao.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u00d4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Ivan Perisic, ng\u01b0\u1eddi v\u1eeba tr\u1ea3i qua m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 World Cup th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u00f9ng \u0110T Croatia. C\u1ef1u HLV Chelsea \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 c\u1ef1c cao t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1989.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cC\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1edf h\u1eefu nh\u1eefng t\u1ed1 ch\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u. T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean l\u00e0 t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ed1t, trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 Perisic\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/ivan-perisic-noi-gi-truoc-loi-moi-goi-toi-mu-cua-mourinho-172-191400.html\" target=\"_blank\">Ivan Perisic n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai</span>, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Inter Milan. \u0110\u00f3 th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u00f2n gi\u00e1ng m\u1ea1nh v\u00e0o tham v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Old Trafford.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>MU d\u00f9ng ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 Perisic</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">MU mu\u1ed1n mua Ivan Perisic c\u1ee7a Inter Milan, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Old Trafford d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ecbnh chi \u0111\u1ee7 62 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng nh\u01b0 ph\u00eda \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Italia y\u00eau c\u1ea7u.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Perisic toi Man United\" title=\"Perisic toi Man United\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/8/2/Ivan-Perisic-noi-gi-truoc-loi-moi-goi-toi-MU-cua-Mourinho--hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>MU d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ecbnh d\u00f9ng ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 Perisic\u00a0</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nH\u00e8 n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i, M.U \u0111\u00e3 3 l\u1ea7n tr\u1ea3 gi\u00e1 cho Perisic, song s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n 35, 44 v\u00e0 48 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng m\u00e0 Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111\u01b0a ra \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb Inter Milan t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i. \u1ede th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Milan \u0111\u00f2i 55 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1989.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nBi\u1ebft \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c M.U v\u1eabn\u00a0 c\u00f3 \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh mua Perisic, Inter \u0111\u00e3 n\u00e2ng gi\u00e1 b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i l\u00ean 62 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Old Trafford s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi ra \u0111\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn Mourinho c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ec3 c\u00f3 kinh ph\u00ed chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Perisic, M.U s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u00e1n Anthony Martial, c\u00f3 tin cho r\u1eb1ng Chelsea \u0111ang nh\u1eafm c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p nh\u01b0 s\u1ef1 thay th\u1ebf cho Eden Hazard, ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Real Madrid \u1edf H\u00e8 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1378","checkdouble":"191494"},{"date":"10:45 18/07","title":"Kante \u0111\u01b0a ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/6/kante-dua-ra-quyet-dinh-ve-tuong-lai.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c th\u00f4ng tin chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng ch\u00e2u \u00c2u m\u00f9a H\u00e8 2018 trong ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay (18/7). Nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u1edbi n\u00f3ng hot nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u00f9a h\u00e8 2018 t\u1eeb c\u00e1c CLB l\u1edbn t\u1ea1i ch\u00e2u \u00c2u.</h2>(li\u00ean t\u1ee5c c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt)<br>\r\n<h2>M.U nh\u1eadn tin m\u1eebng t\u1eeb Toby Alderweireld</h2>\r\nTr\u1edf v\u1ec1 t\u1eeb chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch World Cup 2018 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u00f9ng tuy\u1ec3n B\u1ec9, trung v\u1ec7 Toby Alderweireld b\u00e0y t\u1ecf s\u1ef1 kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1ec1 Tottenham, ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c l\u00e0 HLV Pochettino \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng tin d\u00f9ng anh sau khi tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i t\u1eeb ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng. Tin t\u1ee9c khi\u1ebfn Mourinho v\u00e0 MU ph\u1ea5n kh\u1edfi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\"T\u00f4i d\u1ed3n l\u1ef1c cho World Cup 2018. T\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n ch\u1ee9ng minh \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec \u0111\u00f3 v\u1edbi t\u00f4i, v\u00ec sao tr\u01b0\u1edbc gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u01a1i. \u0110\u00f3 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n l\u00e0 b\u1ea5t c\u00f4ng. T\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n cho th\u1ea5y t\u00f4i v\u1eabn l\u00e0 Toby nh\u01b0 th\u00e1ng 11 (th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m l\u00fac ch\u01b0a b\u1ecb ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng\". H\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a Toby v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng London ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n 1 n\u0103m v\u00e0 anh v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd gia h\u1ea1n.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tin chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00f4m nay ng\u00e0y 187, tin chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Tin chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00f4m nay ng\u00e0y 187, tin chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/12/tottenham-lai-ga-gam-mu-mua-alderweireld.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Alderweireld</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2>Zidane t\u1edbi Juve t\u00e1i ng\u1ed9 Ronaldo</h2>\r\n\u0110\u00e0i ph\u00e1t thanh El Primer Palo (Italy) v\u1eeba khi\u1ebfn d\u01b0 lu\u1eadn s\u1ed1c khi ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 th\u00f4ng tin Zinedine Zidane \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t tho\u1ea3 thu\u1eadn tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Juventus. Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ph\u00e1p s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ea3m nh\u1eadn v\u1ecb tr\u00ed Gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c th\u1ec3 thao. Th\u1eddi gian d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m Zidane s\u1ebd l\u00e0 v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 10/2018. B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh Zidane, Juve c\u00f2n b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m Fabio Paratici - c\u1ef1u tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Italy, l\u00e0m \u0111\u1ed3ng Gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c th\u1ec3 thao.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTh\u00f4ng tin Zidane tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Juve ch\u1ec9 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n v\u00e0i ng\u00e0y sau khi Cristiano Ronaldo c\u00f3 m\u00e0n ra m\u1eaft Juve. N\u1ebfu c\u00f3 th\u00eam Zidane, b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i n\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd t\u1ea1o n\u00ean giai \u0111o\u1ea1n ho\u00e0ng kim ti\u1ebfp theo c\u1ee7a Juve trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed CLB.\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/zidane-sap-tai-ngo-ronaldo-tai-juve-176-191479.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2016/1/7/HLV-Zidane-noi-gi-ve-tuong-lai-Ronaldo-hinh-anh-2.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/zidane-sap-tai-ngo-ronaldo-tai-juve-176-191479.html\">N\u00d3NG: HLV Zidane s\u1eafp t\u00e1i ng\u1ed9 Ronaldo t\u1ea1i Juventus</span><br>\r\n<span>Theo ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng T\u00e2y Ban Nha, HLV Zidane c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c sau khi chia tay Real Madrid. V\u00e0 b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 ti\u1ebfp theo c\u1ee7a Zizou s\u1ebd l\u00e0 CLB...</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Hazard \u0111\u1ea1t tho\u1ea3 thu\u1eadn mi\u1ec7ng v\u1edbi Real Madrid</h2>\r\nNgay sau tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018, Eden Hazard b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd b\u00e0y t\u1ecf mong mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Chelsea \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea7u qu\u00e2n cho m\u1ed9t CLB m\u00e0 anh \u01b0a th\u00edch: \u201cChelsea s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0a ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng - n\u1ebfu h\u1ecd mu\u1ed1n cho t\u00f4i \u0111i, b\u1ea1n bi\u1ebft \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ebfn \u01b0a th\u00edch c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i r\u1ed3i \u0111\u00f3. Sau s\u00e1u n\u0103m tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi \u1edf Chelsea, c\u00f3 l\u1ebd \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ebfn l\u00fac t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i kh\u00e1m ph\u00e1 ra m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t\u201d. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo c\u00e1c ngu\u1ed3n tin, \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ebfn m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 Real Madrid. \u0110\u00e0i RMC Sport (Ph\u00e1p) kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Hazard \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn b\u1eb1ng mi\u1ec7ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Bernabeu. B\u00e2y gi\u1edd, Hazard ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n ch\u1edd k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 tr\u00ean b\u00e0n \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n gi\u1eefa Real v\u00e0 Chelsea.\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/hlv-bi-ung-ho-hazard-bo-chelsea-sang-real-madrid-172-191484.html\">HLV B\u1ec9 \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 Hazard b\u1ecf Chelsea sang Real Madrid</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>PSG kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecb ng\u0103n c\u1ea3n b\u00e1n Neymar v\u00e0 Mbappe</h2>\r\nLuis Fernandez, Gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c c\u1ee7a PSG, cho bi\u1ebft \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecb x\u1eed ph\u1ea1t n\u1ebfu b\u00e1n Neymar ho\u1eb7c Kylian Mbappe trong H\u00e8 n\u00e0y. M\u1ea5y th\u00e1ng qua, PSG b\u1ecb UEFA nghi ng\u1edd vi ph\u1ea1m lu\u1eadt c\u00f4ng b\u1eb1ng t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh (FFP). Tuy nhi\u00ean, cu\u1ed9c \u0111i\u1ec1u tra d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn c\u1ee7a UEFA \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb hu\u1ef7 sau khi c\u01a1 quan n\u00e0y xem x\u00e9t c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3 h\u01a1n gi\u1ea5y t\u1edd.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNeymar \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Real Madrid li\u00ean h\u1ec7. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, Mbappe \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn nh\u00f2m ng\u00f3 sau m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1edf World Cup 2018 c\u00f9ng tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/18/1-neymar.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u00a0</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nChelsea ra gi\u00e1 kh\u1ee7ng mua \"Messi khung g\u1ed7\"</h2>\r\nAlisson l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Liverpool trong n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p. Tuy nhi\u00ean tr\u01b0\u1edbc t\u00ecnh c\u1ea3nh Thibaut Courtois c\u00f3 \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Real, Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1ea3y v\u00e0o cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 si\u00eau sao c\u00f3 bi\u1ec7t danh \"Messi khung g\u1ed7\". Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7, \"The Blues\" tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng 62 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho AS Roma - CLB m\u00e0 Alisson \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o.\r\n<h2>Pavard \u0111\u1eaft h\u00e0ng</h2>\r\nH\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u00e1nh ph\u1ea3i c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p c\u00f3 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n tuy\u1ec7t hay t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u00fd do \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ea1i gia ch\u00e2u \u00c2u mu\u1ed1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y, Hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, Leverkusen \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng t\u1eeb th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1377","checkdouble":"191496"},{"date":"10:51 18/07","title":"FIFA g\u00e2y tranh c\u00e3i v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t World Cup 2018","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/9/huyen-thoai-brazil-bao-ve-thoi-an-va-cua-neymar.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, FIFA \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh ti\u00eau bi\u1ec3u World Cup 2018, v\u1edbi r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u c\u00e1i t\u00ean g\u00e2y tranh c\u00e3i.\r\n</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<h2><br>\r\nX\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh hay nh\u1ea5t World Cup<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div>Sau khi tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft gi\u1eefa Ph\u00e1p vs Croatia kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i, BTC \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 nh\u1eefng gi\u1ea3i th\u01b0\u1edfng c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n. Theo \u0111\u00f3, Luka Modric gi\u00e0nh Qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng v\u00e0ng, Harry Kane c\u00f3 Chi\u1ebfc gi\u00e0y v\u00e0ng, Thibaut Courtois gi\u1eadt G\u0103ng tay v\u00e0ng, trong khi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t gi\u1ea3i g\u1ecdi t\u00ean Kylian Mbappe.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>Nh\u01b0ng trong danh s\u00e1ch 11 c\u00e1i t\u00ean xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t, Courtois v\u00e0 Kane \u0111\u00e3 v\u1eafng b\u00f3ng. V\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng tuy\u1ec3n Anh, \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u1ea3i th\u00edch \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c, khi ch\u1ec9 1/6 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ghi \u1edf v\u00f2ng knock-out. Tuy nhi\u00ean v\u1edbi Courtois, ng\u01b0\u1eddi v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua ch\u00ednh Lloris \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n hay nh\u1ea5t gi\u1ea3i &ndash; l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh ti\u00eau bi\u1ec3u.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\u1ede h\u00e0ng h\u1eadu v\u1ec7, b\u1ed9 t\u1ee9 l\u00e0 Kieran Trippier, Raphael Varane, Dejan Lovren v\u00e0&hellip; Ashley Young. C\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u tranh c\u00e3i v\u1ec1 s\u1ef1 v\u1eafng b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 tr\u00e1i Lucas Hernandez, hay \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a Lovren t\u1ea1i Croatia &ndash; trung v\u1ec7 Vida.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<div style=\"width: 100%;\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh ti\u00eau bi\u1ec3u World Cup 2018\" title=\"thu mon Courtois\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/11/courtois-phat-bieu-sau-tran-phap-10-bi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Courtois kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ecdn v\u00e0o&nbsp;\u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh ti\u00eau bi\u1ec3u World Cup 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div><br>\r\n6 c\u00e1i t\u00ean c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i \u0111a s\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i b\u00e0n c\u00e3i, v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a 3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t gi\u1ea3i l\u00e0 Modric, Hazard v\u00e0 Griezmann. &ldquo;Si\u00eau xe&rdquo; Kylian Mbappe l\u0129nh x\u01b0\u1edbng h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o, nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n h\u1ee3p l\u00fd.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>Nh\u01b0ng \u1edf 2 c\u00e1i t\u00ean c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i, r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u C\u0110V \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch FIFA qu\u00e1 thi\u00ean v\u1ecb \u0110T Brazil, v\u1edbi&hellip; Paulinho v\u00e0 Neymar. S\u1ed1 10 c\u1ee7a Selecao \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 World Cup \u0111\u00e1ng th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng cho d\u00f9 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, b\u1edfi anh \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng x\u1ea5u v\u00ec nh\u1eefng pha \u0103n v\u1ea1 th\u00f4 thi\u1ec3n. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, Ivan Perisic ho\u1eb7c Kevin De Bruyne l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>V\u1edbi Paulinho, nh\u1eefng b\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u00f2n l\u1edbn h\u01a1n n\u1eefa khi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 d\u1eebng b\u01b0\u1edbc \u1edf v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft. 2 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p l\u00e0 N&rsquo;Golo Kante v\u00e0 Paul Pogba \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc h\u01a1n Paulinho, nh\u01b0ng h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 bi\u1ebfn m\u1ea5t m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch kh\u00f3 hi\u1ec3u.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div><strong>D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh ti\u00eau bi\u1ec3u World Cup 2018, theo ti\u00eau ch\u00ed b\u00ecnh ch\u1ecdn c\u1ee7a FIFA<br>\r\n</strong> <br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"FIFA \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh ti\u00eau bi\u1ec3u World Cup 2018\" title=\"\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh ti\u00eau bi\u1ec3u World Cup 2018\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/18/fifa.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh ti\u00eau bi\u1ec3u World Cup 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n<div><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/clip-pogba-coi-tran-dien-thuyet-trong-phong-thay-do-truoc-tran-phap-vs-uruguay-461-191500.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/18/clip-pogba-coi-tran-dien-thuyet-trong-phong-thay-do-truoc-tran-phap-vs-uruguay.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/clip-pogba-coi-tran-dien-thuyet-trong-phong-thay-do-truoc-tran-phap-vs-uruguay-461-191500.html\">Clip Pogba c\u1edfi tr\u1ea7n di\u1ec5n thuy\u1ebft trong ph\u00f2ng thay \u0111\u1ed3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn Ph\u00e1p vs Uruguay</span><br>\r\nPaul Pogba kh\u00f4ng kh\u00e1c g\u00ec m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng khi c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed9ng vi\u00ean, kh\u00edch l\u1ec7 tinh th\u1ea7n c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Ph\u00e1p tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft v\u1edbi Uruguay t\u1ea1i World Cup v\u1eeba...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/world-cup-2018-nhung-tran-cau-va-khoanh-khac-dang-nho-nhat-421-191457.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/17/world-cup-2018-nhung-tran-cau-va-khoanh-khac-dang-nho-nhat.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/world-cup-2018-nhung-tran-cau-va-khoanh-khac-dang-nho-nhat-421-191457.html\">World Cup 2018: Nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u v\u00e0 kho\u1ea3nh kh\u1eafc \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1edb nh\u1ea5t</span><br>\r\nK\u1ef3 \u0111\u1ea1i h\u1ed9i tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i, v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c t\u00ecm ra nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng l\u00e0 th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Didier Deschamps, d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng kho\u1ea3nh kh\u1eafc World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n</div>\r\nNguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div>\r\n</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1376","checkdouble":"191498"},{"date":"10:56 18/07","title":"Tin chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng ng\u00e0y 18/7: M.U nh\u1eadn tin m\u1eebng t\u1eeb Toby Alderweireld","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/12/ngay-hom-nay-187.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c th\u00f4ng tin chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng ch\u00e2u \u00c2u m\u00f9a H\u00e8 2018 trong ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay (18/7). Nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u1edbi n\u00f3ng hot nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u00f9a h\u00e8 2018 t\u1eeb c\u00e1c CLB l\u1edbn t\u1ea1i ch\u00e2u \u00c2u.</h2>(li\u00ean t\u1ee5c c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt)<br>\r\n<h2>M.U nh\u1eadn tin m\u1eebng t\u1eeb Toby Alderweireld</h2>\r\nTr\u1edf v\u1ec1 t\u1eeb chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch World Cup 2018 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u00f9ng tuy\u1ec3n B\u1ec9, trung v\u1ec7 Toby Alderweireld b\u00e0y t\u1ecf s\u1ef1 kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1ec1 Tottenham, ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c l\u00e0 HLV Pochettino \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng tin d\u00f9ng anh sau khi tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i t\u1eeb ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng. Tin t\u1ee9c khi\u1ebfn Mourinho v\u00e0 MU ph\u1ea5n kh\u1edfi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\"T\u00f4i d\u1ed3n l\u1ef1c cho World Cup 2018. T\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n ch\u1ee9ng minh \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec \u0111\u00f3 v\u1edbi t\u00f4i, v\u00ec sao tr\u01b0\u1edbc gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u01a1i. \u0110\u00f3 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n l\u00e0 b\u1ea5t c\u00f4ng. T\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n cho th\u1ea5y t\u00f4i v\u1eabn l\u00e0 Toby nh\u01b0 th\u00e1ng 11 (th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m l\u00fac ch\u01b0a b\u1ecb ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng\". H\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a Toby v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng London ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n 1 n\u0103m v\u00e0 anh v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd gia h\u1ea1n.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tin chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00f4m nay ng\u00e0y 187, tin chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Tin chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00f4m nay ng\u00e0y 187, tin chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/12/tottenham-lai-ga-gam-mu-mua-alderweireld.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Alderweireld</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2>Zidane t\u1edbi Juve t\u00e1i ng\u1ed9 Ronaldo</h2>\r\n\u0110\u00e0i ph\u00e1t thanh El Primer Palo (Italy) v\u1eeba khi\u1ebfn d\u01b0 lu\u1eadn s\u1ed1c khi ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 th\u00f4ng tin Zinedine Zidane \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t tho\u1ea3 thu\u1eadn tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Juventus. Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ph\u00e1p s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ea3m nh\u1eadn v\u1ecb tr\u00ed Gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c th\u1ec3 thao. Th\u1eddi gian d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m Zidane s\u1ebd l\u00e0 v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 10/2018. B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh Zidane, Juve c\u00f2n b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m Fabio Paratici - c\u1ef1u tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Italy, l\u00e0m \u0111\u1ed3ng Gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c th\u1ec3 thao.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTh\u00f4ng tin Zidane tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Juve ch\u1ec9 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n v\u00e0i ng\u00e0y sau khi Cristiano Ronaldo c\u00f3 m\u00e0n ra m\u1eaft Juve. N\u1ebfu c\u00f3 th\u00eam Zidane, b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i n\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd t\u1ea1o n\u00ean giai \u0111o\u1ea1n ho\u00e0ng kim ti\u1ebfp theo c\u1ee7a Juve trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed CLB.\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/zidane-sap-tai-ngo-ronaldo-tai-juve-176-191479.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2016/1/7/HLV-Zidane-noi-gi-ve-tuong-lai-Ronaldo-hinh-anh-2.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/zidane-sap-tai-ngo-ronaldo-tai-juve-176-191479.html\">N\u00d3NG: HLV Zidane s\u1eafp t\u00e1i ng\u1ed9 Ronaldo t\u1ea1i Juventus</span><br>\r\n<span>Theo ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng T\u00e2y Ban Nha, HLV Zidane c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c sau khi chia tay Real Madrid. V\u00e0 b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 ti\u1ebfp theo c\u1ee7a Zizou s\u1ebd l\u00e0 CLB...</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Hazard \u0111\u1ea1t tho\u1ea3 thu\u1eadn mi\u1ec7ng v\u1edbi Real Madrid</h2>\r\nNgay sau tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018, Eden Hazard b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd b\u00e0y t\u1ecf mong mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Chelsea \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea7u qu\u00e2n cho m\u1ed9t CLB m\u00e0 anh \u01b0a th\u00edch: \u201cChelsea s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0a ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng - n\u1ebfu h\u1ecd mu\u1ed1n cho t\u00f4i \u0111i, b\u1ea1n bi\u1ebft \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ebfn \u01b0a th\u00edch c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i r\u1ed3i \u0111\u00f3. Sau s\u00e1u n\u0103m tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi \u1edf Chelsea, c\u00f3 l\u1ebd \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ebfn l\u00fac t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i kh\u00e1m ph\u00e1 ra m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t\u201d. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo c\u00e1c ngu\u1ed3n tin, \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ebfn m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 Real Madrid. \u0110\u00e0i RMC Sport (Ph\u00e1p) kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Hazard \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn b\u1eb1ng mi\u1ec7ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Bernabeu. B\u00e2y gi\u1edd, Hazard ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n ch\u1edd k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 tr\u00ean b\u00e0n \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n gi\u1eefa Real v\u00e0 Chelsea.\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/hlv-bi-ung-ho-hazard-bo-chelsea-sang-real-madrid-172-191484.html\">HLV B\u1ec9 \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 Hazard b\u1ecf Chelsea sang Real Madrid</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>PSG kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecb ng\u0103n c\u1ea3n b\u00e1n Neymar v\u00e0 Mbappe</h2>\r\nLuis Fernandez, Gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c c\u1ee7a PSG, cho bi\u1ebft \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecb x\u1eed ph\u1ea1t n\u1ebfu b\u00e1n Neymar ho\u1eb7c Kylian Mbappe trong H\u00e8 n\u00e0y. M\u1ea5y th\u00e1ng qua, PSG b\u1ecb UEFA nghi ng\u1edd vi ph\u1ea1m lu\u1eadt c\u00f4ng b\u1eb1ng t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh (FFP). Tuy nhi\u00ean, cu\u1ed9c \u0111i\u1ec1u tra d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn c\u1ee7a UEFA \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb hu\u1ef7 sau khi c\u01a1 quan n\u00e0y xem x\u00e9t c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3 h\u01a1n gi\u1ea5y t\u1edd.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNeymar \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Real Madrid li\u00ean h\u1ec7. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, Mbappe \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn nh\u00f2m ng\u00f3 sau m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1edf World Cup 2018 c\u00f9ng tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/18/1-neymar.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u00a0</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nChelsea ra gi\u00e1 kh\u1ee7ng mua \"Messi khung g\u1ed7\"</h2>\r\nAlisson l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Liverpool trong n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p. Tuy nhi\u00ean tr\u01b0\u1edbc t\u00ecnh c\u1ea3nh Thibaut Courtois c\u00f3 \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Real, Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1ea3y v\u00e0o cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 si\u00eau sao c\u00f3 bi\u1ec7t danh \"Messi khung g\u1ed7\". Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7, \"The Blues\" tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng 62 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho AS Roma - CLB m\u00e0 Alisson \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o.\r\n<h2>Pavard \u0111\u1eaft h\u00e0ng</h2>\r\nH\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u00e1nh ph\u1ea3i c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p c\u00f3 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n tuy\u1ec7t hay t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u00fd do \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ea1i gia ch\u00e2u \u00c2u mu\u1ed1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y, Hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, Leverkusen \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng t\u1eeb th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1375","checkdouble":"191501"},{"date":"11:28 18/07","title":"James Rodriguez c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Real ngay m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/25/james-rodriguez-co-the-tro-lai-real-ngay-mua-he-nay.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>R\u1eddi Bernabeu 1 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i, nh\u01b0ng gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 James Rodriguez tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Real Madrid l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nJames chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb v\u1ec1 Real<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ph\u1ea3i ra \u0111i nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 kh\u00e1c v\u00ec kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u, James Rodriguez \u0111\u00e3 gia nh\u1eadp Bayern Munich theo b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n 2 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i. Nh\u01b0ng l\u00fac n\u00e0y, HLV Zidane \u0111\u00e3 r\u1eddi CLB, v\u00e0 c\u00e1nh c\u1eeda tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Real Madrid c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Colombia s\u00e1ng s\u1ee7a h\u01a1n bao gi\u1edd h\u1ebft.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, b\u1ed1 d\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a James &ndash; \u00f4ng Juan Carlos Restrepo \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng chia s\u1ebb v\u1edbi \u0111\u00e0i truy\u1ec1n h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a T\u00e2y Ban Nha, r\u1eb1ng HLV Lopetegui \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ea3o lu\u1eadn v\u1ec1 s\u1ef1 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i. \u00d4ng cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;C\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y 2 tu\u1ea7n, h\u1ecd c\u00f3 trao \u0111\u1ed5i v\u1edbi nhau. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c tr\u00f2 chuy\u1ec7n ng\u1eafn g\u1ecdn nh\u01b0ng r\u1ea5t t\u00edch c\u1ef1c.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111ang ph\u00e2n t\u00edch nh\u1eefng g\u00ec HLV Lopetegui \u0111ang th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n, v\u00e0 t\u00f4i tin r\u1eb1ng phong c\u00e1ch c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng \u1ea5y ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt &ndash; James Rodriguez ch\u1eb3ng h\u1ea1n. S\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 c\u1ee7a Zidane r\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng gi\u00fap Real Madrid tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn. Xem x\u00e9t c\u00e1c s\u1ef1 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i tin r\u1eb1ng James s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi Lopetegui.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"James Rodriguez tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Real Madrid l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3\" title=\"James Rodriguez s\u1ebd ch\u1ed1ng l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/25/james-rodriguez-co-the-tro-lai-real-ngay-mua-he-nay.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>James Rodriguez tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Real Madrid l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div><br>\r\n&ldquo;C\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111ang tr\u1ea3i qua 1 n\u0103m tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi t\u1ea1i Bayern Munich, m\u1ed9t m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng. T\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u1eb1ng, James s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng cam k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Bayern, nh\u01b0ng khi Real Madrid m\u1eddi g\u1ecdi, m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra&rdquo; &ndash; b\u1ed1 d\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a James Rodriguez k\u1ebft lu\u1eadn.</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo \u0111\u00f3, b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 2 n\u0103m c\u1ee7a James v\u1edbi Bayern Munich s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1o h\u1ea1n v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 6/2019, cho ph\u00e9p H\u00f9m x\u00e1m c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 31 tri\u1ec7u euro khi th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n k\u1ebft th\u00fac. Nh\u01b0ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111ang di\u1ec5n ra tr\u00ean th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng, ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng James Rodriguez tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Real Madrid.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Hi\u1ec7n nay, CLB Ho\u00e0ng gia T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u00e3 chia tay Cris Ronaldo, v\u00e0 v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a Gareth Bale. H\u1ecd \u0111ang t\u00ecm c\u00e1ch chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Eden Hazard ngay m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y, v\u00e0 vi\u1ec7c g\u1ecdi tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i James l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111i h\u1ee3p l\u00fd.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/hlv-bi-ung-ho-hazard-bo-chelsea-sang-real-madrid-172-191484.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/15/hlv-bi-ung-ho-hazard-bo-chelsea-sang-real-madrid.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/hlv-bi-ung-ho-hazard-bo-chelsea-sang-real-madrid-172-191484.html\">HLV B\u1ec9 \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 Hazard b\u1ecf Chelsea sang Real Madrid</span><br>\r\nHLV Roberto Martinez khuy\u00ean nh\u1ee7 c\u1eadu h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u01b0ng Eden Hazard n\u00ean t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t h\u01a1n cho s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u1edf tu\u1ed5i 27, thay v\u00ec c\u1ee9 an t\u1ecda \u1edf m\u1ed9t...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/zidane-sap-tai-ngo-ronaldo-tai-juve-176-191479.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2016/1/7/HLV-Zidane-noi-gi-ve-tuong-lai-Ronaldo-hinh-anh-2.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/zidane-sap-tai-ngo-ronaldo-tai-juve-176-191479.html\">N\u00d3NG: HLV Zidane s\u1eafp t\u00e1i ng\u1ed9 Ronaldo t\u1ea1i Juventus</span><br>\r\nTheo ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng T\u00e2y Ban Nha, HLV Zidane c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c sau khi chia tay Real Madrid. V\u00e0 b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 ti\u1ebfp theo c\u1ee7a Zizou s\u1ebd l\u00e0 CLB...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1374","checkdouble":"191502"}]}